ike past the time when HubSpot takes in information.","index":264,"end_time":978.4,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":961.52,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So they had to be manually enrolled, and that''s why the lead source didn''t change.","index":265,"end_time":985.36,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":978.64,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Say that again, sorry.","index":266,"end_time":989.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":987.84,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"You know how the sync has specific times when it happens during the day?","index":267,"end_time":996.56,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":990.64,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"And if, for example, two people decide to fill in a form at a time that''s already past the sync, sometimes it can happen that the system doesn''t track them down.","index":268,"end_time":1009.61,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":996.96,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"And then like, has like the old lead source or has some kind of an old information format.","index":269,"end_time":1015.21,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1009.61,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So then they have to be manually enrolled.","index":270,"end_time":1017.69,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1015.45,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"And that''s the two screenshots that I sent you for.","index":271,"end_time":1022.17,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1017.69,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So if a context is like the reit.","index":272,"end_time":1025.61,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1023.21,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah, the manually refreshing part.","index":273,"end_time":1028.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1026.09,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":274,"end_time":1029.34,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1028.74,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"I don''t have to manually input everything.","index":275,"end_time":1031.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1029.34,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It''s just manually refreshing the workflows.","index":276,"end_time":1034.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1031.02,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So those contacts need to be manually enrolled in remove contact or add contact to hot list and club visited.","index":277,"end_time":1041.78,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1034.42,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"But it''s the same, like, you can see it from the screenshots, like where you can search for contacts.","index":278,"end_time":1049.38,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1042.26,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Okay.","index":279,"end_time":1052.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1051.54,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"If I have more questions, I''ll reach out on that stuff.","index":280,"end_time":1056.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1052.99,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":281,"end_time":1058.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1057.71,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"All right, fine.","index":282,"end_time":1059.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1058.23,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I don''t really have anything else, guys, on my end.","index":283,"end_time":1068.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1063.63,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I. I''m sure I will, as I''m building more lists to make sure that I''m doing them right.","index":284,"end_time":1074.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1069.15,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I''ll.","index":285,"end_time":1075.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1074.99,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I''ll send them over to you guys and then you guys can kind of let me know.","index":286,"end_time":1078.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1075.35,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"How are you?","index":287,"end_time":1081.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1080.63,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"How do you manage the.","index":288,"end_time":1082.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1081.51,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"The 