,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Do you have any based in the.","index":606,"end_time":1992.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1990.89,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Us Our paid ads team is in Mexico.","index":607,"end_time":1997.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1992.13,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And do they, they speak English I''m assuming?","index":608,"end_time":2000.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1998.09,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, completely.","index":609,"end_time":2002.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2000.97,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"What, what, what, what are typical like relation business arrange.","index":610,"end_time":2007.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2002.13,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like what kind of experience do they have and how do they work with clients?","index":611,"end_time":2010.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2007.92,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I mean they manage all of our clients paid activities all across the world.","index":612,"end_time":2015.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2011.2,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Because we had that with ideometry and it kind of sucked.","index":613,"end_time":2020.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2017.52,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like, like they were asking us a question and we didn''t know the answer to.","index":614,"end_time":2023.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2020.72,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We''re looking for.","index":615,"end_time":2024.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2023.96,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, we make recommendations and just get you guys to approve those and then we put them in place and then we run analysis every week and hop into the account to check up on everything, make changes.","index":616,"end_time":2036.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2026,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"If we think is that a separate cost?","index":617,"end_time":2038.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2036.55,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, we could work that into hours.","index":618,"end_time":2040.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2039.19,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Work that into hours.","index":619,"end_time":2042.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2041.11,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Okay.","index":620,"end_time":2042.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2042.11,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And would it be at a different hourly rate than.","index":621,"end_time":2044.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2042.71,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"No, it would be the same hourly rate.","index":622,"end_time":2046.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2045.35,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"How many hours typically a business spend on paid ad management?","index":623,"end_time":2051.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2047.75,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"What''s the range typically between like 8 and 20amonth, depending on how many accounts because we''re in there every week.","index":624,"end_time":2060.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2051.27,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":625,"end_time":2064.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2064.11,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"What kind of businesses use your services for that?","index":626,"end_time":2071.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2067.31,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I mean almost all of our clients have some sort of paid activities going on.","index":627,"end_time":2075.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2071.87,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We do B2C.","index":628,"end_time":2078.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2077.31,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We do B2B.","index":629,"end_time":2078.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2078.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So working in both major markets.","index":630,"end_time":2082.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2080.11,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":631,"end_time":2084.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2084.11,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Who is, is there a person who''s expert who can talk to us?","index":632,"end_time":2088.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2085.08,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I mean.","index":633,"end_time":2089.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2089.16,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s the same as like our web.","index":634,"end_time":2091.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2089.56,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Like me and Nina speak to everything.","index":635,"end_time":2092.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2091.48,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We, we meet with our paid team internally and go through all their notes and, and then pitch that to you guys.","index":636,"end_time":2099.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2093,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And so we don''t meet with the people pressing the buttons.","index":637,"end_time":2102.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2099.72,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We.","index":638,"end_time":2103.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2102.8,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Not typically.","index":639,"end_time":2103.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2103.16,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No.","index":640,"end_time":2104.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2103.96,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":641,"end_time":2105.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2105.32,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We want them to just because we''re, we''re managing our clients every week we want them focused on being in the platforms, not being in meetings.","index":642,"end_time":2114.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2107.72,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":643,"end_time":2116.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2115.92,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Maybe.","index":644,"end_time":2121.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2120.56,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"All right.","index":645,"end_time":2126.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2126.24,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I don''t have anything else.","index":646,"end_time":2127.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2126.72,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I think that''s fine.","index":647,"end_time":2128.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2127.84,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"May come back to this.","index":648,"end_time":2130.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2129.84,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":649,"end_time":2133.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2131.2,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I mean and me and Nina are more than experienced that hop into Meta or Google Ads or LinkedIn ads or anything we''re running.","index":650,"end_time":2139.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2133.52,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean meta would be your guys best channel obviously.","index":651,"end_time":2142.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2139.12,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So.","index":652,"end_time":2142.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2142.38,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":653,"end_time":2146.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2145.94,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"The thing that we find like really important is like fast communication.","index":654,"end_time":2153.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2146.98,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like we talk to our current person, they respond pretty quickly.","index":655,"end_time":2158.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2154.42,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Is that Right.","index":656,"end_time":2158.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2158.42,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Milan, do you feel like they respond quickly to things?","index":657,"end_time":2162.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2158.86,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"The new girl.","index":658,"end_time":2163.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2162.58,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"The new girl.","index":659,"end_time":2164.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2163.86,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"The new Marcela, I think, has been a lot better than what we''ve had in the past.","index":660,"end_time":2168.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2164.58,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":661,"end_time":2169.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2169.18,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"She even gave suggestions today on what we should be changing.","index":662,"end_time":2173.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2170.54,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I think she''s a lot better.","index":663,"end_time":2175.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2174.38,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":664,"end_time":2176.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2176.06,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We might come back.","index":665,"end_time":2177.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2177.1,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I''m just keeping that in our back pocket.","index":666,"end_time":2179.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2177.9,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like, we.","index":667,"end_time":2180.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2179.7,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We want to keep thinking about ads.","index":668,"end_time":2184.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2180.38,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"How do we make ads better?","index":669,"end_time":2185.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2184.3,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And.","index":670,"end_time":2186.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2185.98,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean, even if you just want us to take a couple hours this month to run an audit, that''s something we can do.","index":671,"end_time":2190.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2186.3,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"What.","index":672,"end_time":2191.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2190.94,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"What is in an audit?","index":673,"end_time":2192.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2191.26,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It would basically be examining everything that you guys have been running.","index":674,"end_time":2195.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2192.7,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We typically do like a. I mean, it''s December, so we would look at this year compared to anything from last year and then make recommendations on changes.","index":675,"end_time":2204.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2196.14,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Do you need.","index":676,"end_time":2206.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2205.35,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Would you.","index":677,"end_time":2206.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2206.31,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"You got.","index":678,"end_time":2207.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2206.83,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Do you guys already have access to Meta?","index":679,"end_time":2208.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2207.15,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I don''t think we ever turned it off for you guys.","index":680,"end_time":2211.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2208.71,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, I need to.","index":681,"end_time":2213.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2211.03,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think you turned it off like last month with Josh.","index":682,"end_time":2219.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2214.71,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Oh, maybe not.","index":683,"end_time":2221.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2220.31,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I think it was Josh''s account.","index":684,"end_time":2223.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2221.75,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":685,"end_time":2224.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2223.76,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":686,"end_time":2225.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2225.6,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I can send to you, or if you have your business id, then we can send a request through Nisha.","index":687,"end_time":2234.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2225.92,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think that''s a good idea to do an audit.","index":688,"end_time":2235.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2234.04,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"How do we get a business.","index":689,"end_time":2237.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2236.88,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I don''t know where to find it, but I can log in right now and share screens until we get there.","index":690,"end_time":2246,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2238.24,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"How long will it take?","index":691,"end_time":2247.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2247.12,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like two, three hours to run the audit?","index":692,"end_time":2251.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2247.92,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":693,"end_time":2251.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2251.35,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":694,"end_time":2252.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2252.39,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I mean, it depends on the amount of channels.","index":695,"end_time":2253.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2252.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So if we were just analyzing Meta.","index":696,"end_time":2255.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2253.95,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":697,"end_time":2255.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2255.51,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Probably around that time frame.","index":698,"end_time":2257.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2255.79,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right, here.","index":699,"end_time":2261.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2260.47,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"What do I do?","index":700,"end_time":2263.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2262.95,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So you''re in campaign manager.","index":701,"end_time":2274.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2272.63,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"If you just go to business.facebook.com.","index":702,"end_time":2278.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2275.43,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then.","index":703,"end_time":2289.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2288.95,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right, so it''s loading your page.","index":704,"end_time":2290.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2289.51,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Hey, Milan, Is that.","index":705,"end_time":2302.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2301.75,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"She said, like that $3 per lead thing?","index":706,"end_time":2305.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2302.91,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Is that.","index":707,"end_time":2307.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2306.72,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Is that right?","index":708,"end_time":2308.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2307.52,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And what video did we use for that?","index":709,"end_time":2309.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2308.16,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"You remember in our.","index":710,"end_time":2312.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2311.84,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Marcella, she said some campaign dropped to $3 per lead?","index":711,"end_time":2318,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2313.28,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, that was.","index":712,"end_time":2320.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2319.52,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I.","index":713,"end_time":2323.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2323.12,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"That was for one specific day in December.","index":714,"end_time":2326.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2323.48,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":715,"end_time":2327.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2327.12,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"If.","index":716,"end_time":2330.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2329.76,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Hit settings on the left side down and then business info on the left.","index":717,"end_time":2338.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2330.16,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"There''s your portfolio id.","index":718,"end_time":2344.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2342.9,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So if you can just copy and paste that either into the Zoom Chat or Slack.","index":719,"end_time":2351.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2348.58,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":720,"end_time":2352.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2352.42,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Then we can request access.","index":721,"end_time":2354.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2353.14,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Is this something we do right now or will I get a ping later?","index":722,"end_time":2368.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2365.87,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"You''ll.","index":723,"end_time":2369.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2369.39,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You''ll get an email from HubSpot.","index":724,"end_time":2373.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2370.19,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We are the.","index":725,"end_time":2376.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2375.39,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Agency.","index":726,"end_time":2379.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2378.27,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"You are the brand.","index":727,"end_time":2380.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2379.11,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I just have to toggle a bunch of things on basically.","index":728,"end_time":2385.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2382.92,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But yeah, you''ll get an email.","index":729,"end_time":2388.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2386.92,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"To.","index":730,"end_time":2390.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2390.44,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Grant our Request.","index":731,"end_time":2392.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2391.16,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"One of the admins will.","index":732,"end_time":2397.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2395.64,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":733,"end_time":2397.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2397.08,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"An admin on the account will.","index":734,"end_time":2398.839,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2397.4,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So it''s set to go to yifa Y hat Invest.","index":735,"end_time":2401.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2399.64,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You want me to switch that to someone else?","index":736,"end_time":2403,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2401.56,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No, that''s fine.","index":737,"end_time":2404.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2403,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Well, am I getting it right now?","index":738,"end_time":2405.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2404.36,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So I''m sending it.","index":739,"end_time":2407.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2406.2,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s probably going to make me.","index":740,"end_time":2408.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2407.64,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":741,"end_time":2409.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2408.96,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Says that it went through.","index":742,"end_time":2412.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2411.36,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I can also if you just click this link that I''m dropping in the zoom chat, that should be the same thing.","index":743,"end_time":2418.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2412.56,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You''ve received a business partner request.","index":744,"end_time":2422.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2420.96,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Okay.","index":745,"end_time":2423.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2422.8,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Viewer request.","index":746,"end_time":2424.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2423.92,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Okay.","index":747,"end_time":2433.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2432.48,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So basically just pick the pages in the ad accounts to allow us into.","index":748,"end_time":2452.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2448.49,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You have to hit the permissions on the right side.","index":749,"end_time":2456.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2454.57,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"There''s a button at the.","index":750,"end_time":2460.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2459.29,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Or there''s a toggle at the bottom of that list.","index":751,"end_time":2461.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2460.33,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s just full.","index":752,"end_time":2462.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2461.97,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You need full here.","index":753,"end_time":2466.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2464.33,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I mean we would at least need.","index":754,"end_time":2467.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2466.25,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Ads and leads switch to manage everything except sensitive actions.","index":755,"end_time":2474.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2467.85,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"That''s typically what our clients give us.","index":756,"end_time":2476.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2474.89,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"To do the audit.","index":757,"end_time":2478.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2477.29,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":758,"end_time":2480.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2479.53,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It.","index":759,"end_time":2488.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2488.26,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay, so now if you just hit review accept, then that should reflect on our end in a minute or two.","index":760,"end_time":2525.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2516.91,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"When do you think we can get the results by?","index":761,"end_time":2529.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2526.83,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I mean next week.","index":762,"end_time":2531.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2530.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":763,"end_time":2533.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2532.59,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And do you have a.","index":764,"end_time":2534.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2533.87,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Do you have a process for this that''s pretty standard or do you need some direction from us?","index":765,"end_time":2538.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2534.67,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"No, we have a pretty standard.","index":766,"end_time":2540.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2539.24,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean we''re going to go in and examine everything in the meta account.","index":767,"end_time":2542.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2540.28,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":768,"end_time":2544.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2543.48,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I think the recommendations, like it''s.","index":769,"end_time":2547.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2545.08,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We have someone else obviously running this.","index":770,"end_time":2550.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2548.6,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Milan, like what''s on your mind when it comes to like questions?","index":771,"end_time":2553.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2550.88,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"You like to know either how we do things or the result of what we do, or I think a little bit of both.","index":772,"end_time":2562.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2553.52,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I want to be a little more knowledgeable on.","index":773,"end_time":2565.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2563.4,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"On why we make certain changes to ads and the effects that they''re going to have.","index":774,"end_time":2572.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2565.48,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Also want to know just whether we''re doing things efficiently.","index":775,"end_time":2577.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2574.74,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"For me, it sounds like we''re activating and deactivating quite a few different ad sets and campaigns.","index":776,"end_time":2588.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2580.18,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It doesn''t seem to be that efficient.","index":777,"end_time":2590.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2588.42,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"We have very like, we have very aggressive like sales goals going into 2026.","index":778,"end_time":2599.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2592.74,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So our lead count needs to go up and our quality of lead needs to go up as well.","index":779,"end_time":2606.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2601.46,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Are you able to share your goals?","index":780,"end_time":2607.899,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2606.58,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Because that could also influence our audit.","index":781,"end_time":2610.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2607.899,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I can.","index":782,"end_time":2611.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2611.06,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, I''ll send that over.","index":783,"end_time":2614.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2611.86,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, that''d be great.","index":784,"end_time":2615.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2614.42,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":785,"end_time":2616.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2616.18,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I mean like major goal is 4,000 members per club and what that looks like is about 900 or 800 new members in Fort Lauderdale and it''s a thousand four hundred new members net for both of those in Miami.","index":786,"end_time":2635.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2616.66,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So they''re very aggressive and we want to get there, but we know that there''s going to have to be additional spend going into it, and we need to be very efficient with how we, how we do this.","index":787,"end_time":2647.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2636.32,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So put into like a little bit more concretely, we''re getting maybe a dozen leads a day.","index":788,"end_time":2654.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2647.86,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We need to find a way to get up to like 30 plus leads a day.","index":789,"end_time":2659.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2656.26,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And it''s a combination of more funding, more ads, money budget, plus different types of ads.","index":790,"end_time":2669.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2660.98,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like we need to look at that.","index":791,"end_time":2672.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2669.94,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We don''t do Google.","index":792,"end_time":2674.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2672.93,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We tried before with Iam over.","index":793,"end_time":2675.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2674.05,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I think maybe you guys know, it was like $70 a leader, something crazy like that.","index":794,"end_time":2679.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2675.81,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We don''t do any LinkedIn.","index":795,"end_time":2681.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2680.05,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We have an Instagram page where we have.","index":796,"end_time":2684.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2682.05,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I think you should be able to see that.","index":797,"end_time":2686.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2685.25,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But there''s not.","index":798,"end_time":2687.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2686.81,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So that''s it.","index":799,"end_time":2692.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2690.85,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"How do we triple the number of leads we get a day is what''s going to get us there.","index":800,"end_time":2698.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2693.49,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We, at one point, I think we did have maybe a year ago, if you could back look in like, I want to say it''s 2024.","index":801,"end_time":2707.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2698.95,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We had some months, we had like hundreds of leads, like 4, 500 leads, maybe even 800 leads from social media.","index":802,"end_time":2715.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2708.23,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And we''re now like 300 is like a good.","index":803,"end_time":2720.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2715.59,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"3 to 400 is like a good month.","index":804,"end_time":2723.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2722.24,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But I wonder, like, why can''t we get a thousand leads here?","index":805,"end_time":2727.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2723.52,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Because I don''t think we spent all that much more in 2024.","index":806,"end_time":2732.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2727.84,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":807,"end_time":2734.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2733.36,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And part of it is a numbers game, but part of it''s also, you know, if you get 12 a day just to use your numbers and all 12 of them actually become members versus 30 a day and still only 12 of them become members, then, you know, looking at the cost per lead there can.","index":808,"end_time":2746.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2734.08,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I don''t think we''ve.","index":809,"end_time":2747.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2747.04,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I don''t think there''s a lot of things we do, you know, social media we don''t get.","index":810,"end_time":2754.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2748.68,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s not like we can just do some one trick and it convert 50.","index":811,"end_time":2759.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2755.64,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So it is.","index":812,"end_time":2760.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2759.88,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We need more people in because our staff can handle the leads.","index":813,"end_time":2767.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2760.52,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We can call them.","index":814,"end_time":2768.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2767.2,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":815,"end_time":2768.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2768.52,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s just getting.","index":816,"end_time":2769.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2768.84,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We''re not going to get there because we.","index":817,"end_time":2771.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2770.2,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s not realistic.","index":818,"end_time":2772.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2771.6,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Expect we can convert 50% of social media.","index":819,"end_time":2775.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2772.4,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So we were guessing it''s like 10 to 15%.","index":820,"end_time":2778.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2775.85,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":821,"end_time":2779.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2779.01,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I was speaking more to like just minimalizing any spam from Facebook, which is just inherent with the platform.","index":822,"end_time":2786.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2779.33,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Like a junk lead.","index":823,"end_time":2789.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2788.61,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Like a junk lead coming in.","index":824,"end_time":2790.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2789.49,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":825,"end_time":2791.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2790.93,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And then one other question is, do you guys have a sense of like your churn rate.","index":826,"end_time":2797.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2792.93,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So you''re looking to grow both clubs.","index":827,"end_time":2799.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2797.57,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You know, if you''re looking to grow 800 members in one, what are you also like expecting from just past year''s performance of?","index":828,"end_time":2806.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2800.06,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''re probably also going to have maybe this many members leave.","index":829,"end_time":2808.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2806.34,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we''re, we''re expecting it to go down a little, but if it doesn''t, it''s in Miami.","index":830,"end_time":2814.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2810.46,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It''s going to be about 150 over the year.","index":831,"end_time":2817.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2814.62,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"No, no, 150amonth.","index":832,"end_time":2820.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2818.7,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":833,"end_time":2821.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2820.62,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Members leaving.","index":834,"end_time":2822.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2821.66,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So it''s that 2,000 people leave.","index":835,"end_time":2826.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2824.22,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We''d have like 2,000 people leave this gym by the end of the year.","index":836,"end_time":2831,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2826.8,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So we need to bring in 3,000 to get a thousand more.","index":837,"end_time":2837.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2831.16,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":838,"end_time":2839,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2838.6,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So our goal is going to be like 45.","index":839,"end_time":2842.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2839.48,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like 3,500.","index":840,"end_time":2843.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2842.12,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yep.","index":841,"end_time":2844.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2844.28,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"People.","index":842,"end_time":2845.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2844.88,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yep.","index":843,"end_time":2846.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2845.88,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"All right, well, we have access, so we''ll go in and we''ll conduct the audit and we''ll have our recommendations and everything in there.","index":844,"end_time":2851.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2846.92,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I another thing here, it''s not really related to Meta, but in, in other gyms that Robert and I have worked in, a large number of leads come from our website and currently it''s.","index":845,"end_time":2867.929,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2852.93,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"That''s a very low number.","index":846,"end_time":2869.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2867.929,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So maybe doing some kind of like research on, on why that''s happening.","index":847,"end_time":2873.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2870.37,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I mean, obviously we''re redoing the website and that kind of stuff, but is it Google Ads that needs to happen and we''re not currently doing it?","index":848,"end_time":2883.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2874.05,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"That kind of stuff?","index":849,"end_time":2884.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2883.74,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"That would be helpful too.","index":850,"end_time":2886.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2885.58,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean there''d be a few things in there.","index":851,"end_time":2888.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2887.1,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I mean, if the Facebook ads are currently set up as a lead gen form on Facebook, then they wouldn''t even visit the website.","index":852,"end_time":2894.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2888.78,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Two, we''ve talked a lot about like the website''s just not all.","index":853,"end_time":2898.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2895.5,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s not set up very well to convert anyone and there''s not a lot of content on there that would drive them there organically unless they''re searching directly for the club name.","index":854,"end_time":2907.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2898.42,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So a few things there.","index":855,"end_time":2909.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2908.83,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You don''t really have a lot of organic traffic because you would have to have a lot of SEO content for it to show up on Google organically.","index":856,"end_time":2917.91,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2909.63,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"And then that would mean like having blogs in regards to, you know, workouts, trainings or things like that.","index":857,"end_time":2925.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2917.91,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So it would require a lot of in house work for copy, but also an SEO audit.","index":858,"end_time":2931.95,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2925.15,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So for example, if you''re working in Framer, you would need your developer to also work with somebody who''s going to make an SEO audit.","index":859,"end_time":2938.59,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2931.95,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So you have all your methods, descriptions, all your keywords, everything that''s going to rank on Google.","index":860,"end_time":2943.37,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2938.59,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Already ready when the webpage is done.","index":861,"end_time":2945.85,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2943.37,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"I. I think you guys did an audit of our website a few months ago, and it was.","index":862,"end_time":2953.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2947.69,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"One of the things we learned was like, people spend a lot of time on the website.","index":863,"end_time":2957.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2954.33,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We had.","index":864,"end_time":2960.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2959.69,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I think it was like we had an unusually low bounce rate and people were spending like upwards of two minutes, a minute and a half on it.","index":865,"end_time":2970.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2960.21,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So is.","index":866,"end_time":2972.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2971.1,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Do you guys have the analytics on our current website?","index":867,"end_time":2975.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2973.18,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":868,"end_time":2975.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2975.58,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Or is it.","index":869,"end_time":2977.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2976.22,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Is it.","index":870,"end_time":2977.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2977.1,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Is there a Google.","index":871,"end_time":2978.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2977.38,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, I think there''s Google Analytics there.","index":872,"end_time":2981.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2979.02,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"There was.","index":873,"end_time":2982.379,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2981.78,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Can you look at that?","index":874,"end_time":2986.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2985.66,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"One of the main issues was that your desktop version was okay, but the mobile version was not.","index":875,"end_time":2993.58,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2986.5,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Right.","index":876,"end_time":2994.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2993.84,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Working really well.","index":877,"end_time":2995.52,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2994.4,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Can you just.","index":878,"end_time":2997.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2996.24,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Part of this.","index":879,"end_time":2997.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2997.04,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Can you look at the site?","index":880,"end_time":2999.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2997.56,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But don''t.","index":881,"end_time":3000.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2999.2,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"No need to.","index":882,"end_time":3000.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3000.04,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I don''t want you to spend a ton of hours here because we''re going to end up kind of doing things differently.","index":883,"end_time":3005.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3000.68,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I think the question I have here is, is I hear everything we''re saying, but are there things that we should.","index":884,"end_time":3017.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3005.52,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Do we have any.","index":885,"end_time":3020.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3019.6,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Are there any, like, positives about the current site that we should try to emulate into the new rebuild?","index":886,"end_time":3027.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3020.78,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Because I, I was surprised that it was like more than 60% of our visitors were staying over a minute and a half.","index":887,"end_time":3035.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3028.62,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I don''t know if that''s still true.","index":888,"end_time":3036.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3035.7,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So, yeah, whether or not they convert is a different thing.","index":889,"end_time":3041.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3037.82,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But that''s interesting why they''re spending a minute and 63 and that''s high in my mind.","index":890,"end_time":3045.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3041.58,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like you think.","index":891,"end_time":3046.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3045.94,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I think what he said, like, a lot of times it''s like 30 seconds.","index":892,"end_time":3048.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3046.66,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Why are they spending more than a minute?","index":893,"end_time":3050.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3048.98,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So I want to know, like, some of the positives so that way we don''t end up doing too, like we''re able to know why that''s the case and we can still hold on to that.","index":894,"end_time":3061.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3050.99,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":895,"end_time":3061.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3061.23,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Why they''re staying on.","index":896,"end_time":3062.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3061.87,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And I think it was also like, we do have how many people visit the site monthly and it was high.","index":897,"end_time":3069.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3062.83,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Obviously, the only part is the conversion.","index":898,"end_time":3071.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3070.03,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"So are we really trying to bring more people to the site to.","index":899,"end_time":3076.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3072.11,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Or.","index":900,"end_time":3077.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3076.84,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Or is a hypothesis that if we do these changes, it will convert better?","index":901,"end_time":3082.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3077.24,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And yeah, I mean, my guess is that the inbound will bring people to the site, but I don''t know if people.","index":902,"end_time":3088.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3083.8,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"If the problem is if the priority.","index":903,"end_time":3091.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3088.52,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":904,"end_time":3091.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3091.12,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"If the priority is like, first thing is get more people to the site or is it that the.","index":905,"end_time":3096.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3091.44,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"The conversion.","index":906,"end_time":3096.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3096.08,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We need to think about how to get people''s contact information faster or easier than the current site is doing.","index":907,"end_time":3105.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3096.92,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, I Mean, I think we need to take a holistic view of it.","index":908,"end_time":3108.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3106.37,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I would.","index":909,"end_time":3109.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3108.85,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"My gut would tell me that a lot of people going to the site right now are current members, and that definitely would influence their time on page because they''re probably looking for classes and things like that.","index":910,"end_time":3117.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3109.73,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Did you see that in any way?","index":911,"end_time":3119.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3117.97,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Because they''re HubSpot, we have their names and emails.","index":912,"end_time":3122.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3119.65,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But also keep in mind that the old website didn''t have, like, an address, a phone you could, you know, call.","index":913,"end_time":3128.73,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3122.45,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So it could be that people were looking for information for a longer period of time than they usually do.","index":914,"end_time":3134.97,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3128.89,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Okay.","index":915,"end_time":3138.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3137.69,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":916,"end_time":3142.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3142.65,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"From an analytics standpoint, we wouldn''t be able to differentiate between members and non members on the site.","index":917,"end_time":3148.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3142.97,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":918,"end_time":3151.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3150.65,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But I wouldn''t want that number to go down.","index":919,"end_time":3154.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3152.65,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I wouldn''t want necessarily people''s numbers to go.","index":920,"end_time":3157.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3154.63,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"They''re on our site.","index":921,"end_time":3158.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3157.91,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"It''s a good thing.","index":922,"end_time":3159.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3158.55,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah, I agree.","index":923,"end_time":3161.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3159.91,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think.","index":924,"end_time":3161.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3161.03,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean, that''s why I''m saying holistic.","index":925,"end_time":3162.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3161.43,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think we need to build it for new potential prospects and also current members.","index":926,"end_time":3168.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3162.83,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":927,"end_time":3169.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3168.95,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"All right.","index":928,"end_time":3172.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3171.59,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Well, yeah, take just another review of that, if you can, with the ads.","index":929,"end_time":3177.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3172.11,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"I only.","index":930,"end_time":3181.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3179.83,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Only to the point where you.","index":931,"end_time":3182.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3181.46,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"You think you''ve already done the website audit before because that''s how you were able to kind of even have the conference.","index":932,"end_time":3188.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3182.82,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"We think this and that, so I don''t want to redo do that work, but maybe just look at the analytics again and see where do you think there are.","index":933,"end_time":3194.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3188.5,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"What.","index":934,"end_time":3195.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3195.3,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"What metrics are positive that we need to think about?","index":935,"end_time":3198.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3195.66,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Like, well, what''s driving that?","index":936,"end_time":3199.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3198.3,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"And what do we need to.","index":937,"end_time":3200.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3199.42,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"What are some of those gaps that we see?","index":938,"end_time":3202.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3200.9,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":939,"end_time":3203.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3203.06,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"From a data perspective.","index":940,"end_time":3204.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3203.54,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Right.","index":941,"end_time":3204.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3204.74,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Because before, I think all we had was, like, kind of feelings about how things look.","index":942,"end_time":3209.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3204.98,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"But we could look at the data one more time.","index":943,"end_time":3213.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3211.22,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Yep.","index":944,"end_time":3214.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3213.46,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right, I''m good.","index":945,"end_time":3217.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3216.5,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Cool.","index":946,"end_time":3219.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3218.58,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Milan, anything else from your end?","index":947,"end_time":3221.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3220.18,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Not for me.","index":948,"end_time":3226.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3225.46,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"No, I was getting my charger.","index":949,"end_time":3227.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3226.22,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Thank you, guys.","index":950,"end_time":3228.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3227.62,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I appreciate your time.","index":951,"end_time":3229.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3228.3,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, of course.","index":952,"end_time":3230.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3229.54,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right, have a great rest of your day.","index":953,"end_time":3231.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3230.34,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Ev, I''ll try and get the make number back to you today.","index":954,"end_time":3235.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3232.61,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, perfect.","index":955,"end_time":3236.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3235.41,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"All right, thank you.","index":956,"end_time":3237.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3236.13,"speaker_name":"Yefei Jin"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":957,"end_time":3238.45,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3237.89,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Bye.","index":958,"end_time":3238.85,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3238.45,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"}],"dateString":"2025-12-17T16:00:00.000Z","host_email":"colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com","meeting_link":"https://us02web.zoom.us/j/86061042503?pwd=x0TBEgRs7qFmrRIEItauCzbH71kaq8.1","participants":["yefei@yhatinvest.com,alex.white@yhatinvest.com,tatiana@powerhousegymsoflo.com,wyattc@yhatinvest.com,robert.rudder@powerhousesoflo.com,colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com,tatiana.fernandez@powerhousesoflo.com,milan.wagner@powerhousesoflo.com,nina.belina@marketersindemand.com,cristina@pgmia.com,milan@pgmia.com","yefei@yhatinvest.com","alex.white@yhatinvest.com","tatiana@powerhousegymsoflo.com","wyattc@yhatinvest.com","robert.rudder@powerhousesoflo.com","tatiana.fernandez@powerhousesoflo.com","milan.wagner@powerhousesoflo.com","nina.belina@marketersindemand.com","cristina@pgmia.com","milan@pgmia.com"],"transcript_url":"https://app.fireflies.ai/view/01KC4WAEM4ZKWGT7D0Q1FYZAM8","organizer_email":"colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com"}'::jsonb,
    '{"label":"positive","confidence":0.92,"bullets":["Approved new SMS automation at $600/month; Milan to lead HubSpot setup with Colin''s team.","Decided to reduce Make.com operations plan from 500K to 150K to save costs.","Colin to deliver Meta ads audit next week; access granted and goals shared.","Team agreed email opt-in checkbox should be mandatory despite potential unsubscribes.","Website rebuild to proceed on Framer with HubSpot integration; audit to preserve strengths."],"highlights":[{"quote":"We need to put a lot more investment into marketing to make that happen.","speaker":"Yefei Jin"},{"quote":"Perfect. I like it.","speaker":"Milan Wagner"},{"quote":"I think we can definitely lower the amount of credits that we''re paying.","speaker":"Colin Costigan"}],"topics":["delivery","marketing","automation","budget","email","ads"],"model":"openai/gpt-4-1106-preview","version":1,"generated_at":"2025-12-17T14:37:00Z"}'::jsonb,
    '{"fireflies_summary":{"notes":"## **Lead Generation and Marketing Communications**\n\nThe team decided to make the marketing communication opt-in checkbox mandatory to ensure leads can be reached effectively.\n\n- **Marketing communication consent will be mandatory** on waiver forms to maximize outreach potential to prospects (07:18)  \n    - Nina Belina confirmed this is legal if unsubscribe options are clear and accessible.  \n    - Milan Wagner emphasized that leads who don''t opt in cannot be marketed to, which defeats the volume-driven business model.  \n    - HubSpot automatically tracks unsubscribes and opt-outs, helping monitor communication health.  \n    - Colin Costigan advised monitoring unsubscribe rates to avoid HubSpot flagging the domain for spam.  \n\n- **Milan Wagner will create segmented lists** to track unsubscribes and opt-outs for ongoing monitoring (10:38)  \n    - This will complement HubSpot’s automatic tracking to keep unsubscribe rates manageable.  \n    - The team agreed to watch the \"email health\" metric in HubSpot, which uses green, yellow, and red zones to signal risk levels.  \n    - Current unsubscribe rate from a recent 6,500-email blast was **0.99%**, considered acceptable (13:18).  \n    - Milan and Colin will ensure that unsubscribed contacts are excluded from future campaigns.  \n\n- **Email marketing contacts are managed manually by toggling status monthly** to free up marketing contact slots for new leads (18:00)  \n    - Milan explained that former members are removed from marketing contacts at month-end to prioritize active prospects.  \n    - This manual process aligns marketing capacity with campaign timing and monthly promotions.  \n\n## **Integrations, Syncing, and System Costs**\n\nThe team reviewed current integration usage and explored opportunities to reduce monthly operational costs.\n\n- **Current Make integration operations are underused compared to plan, allowing cost reduction** (20:40)  \n    - The plan allows **500,000 operations per month**, but only about **55,000 operations** are used with 22 days left in the cycle.  \n    - Colin Costigan expects they can reduce to a **150,000 operation plan costing $116/month** after developers verify usage.  \n    - Yefei Jin requested tracking usage for October and November to set a cost-effective limit with a buffer.  \n    - Colin will provide a recommendation for a lower tier plan based on verified data.  \n\n- **The team has a rollover balance of 42 consulting hours monthly with Colin’s firm** (22:28)  \n    - These hours can be prioritized for website development, HubSpot integrations, or marketing automation.  \n    - Yefei Jin emphasized focusing on HubSpot automation first, as internal developers are handling Framer website work.  \n    - Colin confirmed asynchronous communication works well to accelerate project completion within available hours.  \n\n## **Website Strategy and Analytics**\n\nThe group agreed to rebuild the website with emphasis on HubSpot integration and SEO improvements, while preserving positive user engagement elements.\n\n- **A new website will be developed using Framer with Shopify integration and HubSpot connectivity** (22:49)  \n    - Colin Costigan’s team can handle design, development, and integration without requiring weekly meetings.  \n    - Milan and Yefei emphasized using existing templates to reduce build time and then customizing for smooth animations and functionality.  \n    - Nina Belina highlighted the need for SEO audits and content creation focused on keywords, meta descriptions, and blog posts to drive organic traffic.  \n\n- **Current website analytics show strong engagement but low lead conversion** (48:07)  \n    - Yefei Jin noted visitors spend over a minute and a half on the site, which is unusually high and positive.  \n    - Colin and Nina suggested this might reflect current members seeking info, affecting engagement metrics.  \n    - They recommended a holistic rebuild to cater to both prospects and members, maintaining positive site elements while improving conversion.  \n    - SEO and user experience improvements will target increasing organic traffic and capturing more lead info faster.  \n\n## **Marketing Automation and SMS Implementation**\n\nThe team committed to implementing automated SMS workflows with strict opt-out tracking to improve lead follow-up and compliance.\n\n- **A $600/month SMS automation service will be activated immediately** to trigger messages based on user actions like form fills or club visits (25:32)  \n    - Milan Wagner will lead project management with Colin Costigan and Nina Belina to implement SMS workflows in HubSpot.  \n    - Automation will include triggers for visits, sign-ups, and non-joining prospects to increase engagement.  \n    - The team stressed the importance of logging opt-outs manually in HubSpot when users text “stop” through Air Call, since full sync is limited (27:38).  \n    - Colin proposed adding a checkbox in HubSpot to mark contacts as opted out of texts to prevent further messaging.  \n\n- **Legal risk from improper SMS opt-outs is recognized, driving compliance focus** (28:22)  \n    - Yefei Jin recalled prior legal issues and requested strict controls to avoid lawsuits.  \n    - The team agreed to prioritize these automations and dedicate consulting hours to finish setup before the busy January-February period.  \n\n## **Paid Advertising and Lead Generation Goals**\n\nThe team plans to conduct a paid ads audit and increase ad spend to triple daily lead volume, aiming for aggressive membership growth.\n\n- **A paid ads audit will be conducted next week to optimize campaigns and reduce cost per lead** (36:30)  \n    - Colin Costigan’s team will review Meta campaigns, comparing 2024 data to prior years.  \n    - Milan Wagner expressed a need to understand ad changes’ impact and improve efficiency, since current lead generation is inconsistent.  \n    - Yefei Jin set a target to increase leads from about **12 per day to 30+ per day** through higher budgets and different ad types.  \n    - They noted past Google Ads efforts were too expensive (up to $70 per lead), and currently no LinkedIn ads are running.  \n\n- **Membership growth targets require aggressive lead volume and quality improvements** (43:36)  \n    - Milan shared goals of **4,000 members per club**, requiring approximately **800–1,400 net new members** in key markets annually.  \n    - Yefei explained the churn of roughly **150 members leaving per month** in Miami means gross sign-ups must exceed churn by about 3,500 annually.  \n    - Colin stressed the importance of balancing lead quantity with lead quality to maximize conversion rates.  \n    - The team recognized social media leads convert at about 10–15%, so volume increases are crucial to growth.  \n\n- **Website lead generation is underperforming, prompting plans for SEO and conversion improvements** (47:26)  \n    - Milan noted that other gyms generate many leads from websites, but their current site delivers low numbers.  \n    - Colin and Nina pointed out that current Facebook lead gen forms bypass the website, and the site lacks content for organic Google traffic.  \n    - SEO improvements including blogs and technical audits will support better organic search visibility alongside paid efforts.  \n\n## **Process and Reporting Improvements**\n\nThe team refined lead source tracking, list management, and reporting workflows to improve data accuracy and operational efficiency.\n\n- **Manual enrollment is required for leads missed by automated syncs due to timing gaps** (16:00)  \n    - Nina explained that late form submissions can miss sync windows, causing outdated lead source data.  \n    - Milan clarified this requires refreshing workflows and manually enrolling contacts to update segments properly.  \n    - Screenshots and guides were provided to Milan for managing manual enrollments and hot list segments.  \n\n- **Milan is managing lists independently and will seek help as needed for reports** (14:22)  \n    - He confirmed list creation is working well, while report building depends on available dashboard slots.  \n    - Nina sent tutorials and screenshots supporting manual enrollment and dashboard updates.  \n\n- **Collin and Milan agreed to monitor HubSpot sync and email list health continuously** (10:13)  \n    - This ensures communication metrics stay within acceptable limits and protects domain reputation.  \n    - Milan will track unsubscribe trends and coordinate with Colin if issues arise.","outline":null,"keywords":["HubSpot","SMS automation","Paid Ads Audit","Lead Generation","Website Redevelopment","Marketing Communication Opt-Out"],"overview":"- **Mandatory Marketing Consent:** Opt-in checkbox on waiver forms is required to improve lead outreach and ensure legal compliance.  \n- **Email Unsubscribe Monitoring:** Milan will create segmented lists to track unsubscribes; current rate is 0.99%, acceptable for campaigns.  \n- **Integration Cost Reduction:** Underused integration plan allows for a switch to a lower tier, reducing costs significantly to $116/month.  \n- **Website Rebuild Focus:** New site will enhance HubSpot integration and SEO while maintaining user engagement to boost lead conversion.  \n- **SMS Automation Implementation:** $600/month service for automated SMS workflows to enhance follow-ups, compliance is critical to avoid legal issues.  \n- **Aggressive Lead Generation Target:** Aim to increase daily leads from 12 to 30+, focusing on both volume and quality for membership growth.","action_items":"\n**Milan Wagner**\nMake marketing communications checkbox mandatory in waiver forms and monitor opt-outs/unsubscribes using segmented lists in HubSpot (06:00)\nReach out to HubSpot rep to set up SMS automation contract and manage its onboarding process (30:40)\nLead project management of SMS automation collaboration with Colin and Nina to ensure timely setup before January peak (28:30)\nManage manual enrollments in HubSpot workflows to correct lead source data and lists (15:00)\nShare 2026 aggressive membership goals with Colin to inform paid ads audit and campaign strategy (43:31)\nCoordinate with Colin and Nina on HubSpot lists and workflows to optimize lead management and marketing contact limits (14:22)\n\n**Yefei Jin**\nProvide Facebook Business Manager business ID for paid ads audit access and confirm admin approval (38:39)\nOversee approval of the SMS automation budget (~$600/month) and prioritize initial contract signing (25:32)\nFacilitate prioritization of hourly support resources toward HubSpot SMS automation rather than website build (22:45)\nCoordinate and approve paid ads audit scope and support audit development (36:30)\nMonitor audit output next week and decide further marketing initiatives based on results (42:10)\n\n**Colin Costigan**\nVerify Make (Integromat) operations usage with developers for potential subscription cost reduction (20:10)\nAssist with HubSpot SMS automation setup, including workflow triggers and content, and create opted-out checkbox for text messaging compliance (26:00)\nLead paid ads audit for Meta platforms, deliver recommendations following December (36:30)\nSupport integration and access approvals for Facebook Business Manager (38:39)\nConsult on website rebuild including HubSpot integration requirements and overall marketing strategy (47:30)\n\n**Nina Belina**\nProvide tutorials and screenshot guides for workflows, lead gen forms, and manual enrollment in HubSpot (14:54)\nAdvise on email health metrics and HubSpot compliance monitoring (11:58)\nCollaborate on the auditing and strategy implementation for SEO and website conversion improvement (48:00)\nSupport SMS automation setup and opt-out process alongside Colin and Milan (26:00)\n"},"migrated_from":"contract_meetings","original_id":"18b46c39-849f-4bf4-8f24-89deb71eff42","master_marketer":{"status":"migrated"}}'::jsonb,
