  '[{"text":"Make marketing communications checkbox mandatory in waiver forms and monitor opt-outs/unsubscribes using segmented lists in HubSpot (06:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Reach out to HubSpot rep to set up SMS automation contract and manage its onboarding process (30:40)","completed":false},{"text":"Lead project management of SMS automation collaboration with Colin and Nina to ensure timely setup before January peak (28:30)","completed":false},{"text":"Manage manual enrollments in HubSpot workflows to correct lead source data and lists (15:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Share 2026 aggressive membership goals with Colin to inform paid ads audit and campaign strategy (43:31)","completed":false},{"text":"Coordinate with Colin and Nina on HubSpot lists and workflows to optimize lead management and marketing contact limits (14:22)","completed":false},{"text":"Provide Facebook Business Manager business ID for paid ads audit access and confirm admin approval (38:39)","completed":false},{"text":"Oversee approval of the SMS automation budget (~$600/month) and prioritize initial contract signing (25:32)","completed":false},{"text":"Facilitate prioritization of hourly support resources toward HubSpot SMS automation rather than website build (22:45)","completed":false},{"text":"Coordinate and approve paid ads audit scope and support audit development (36:30)","completed":false},{"text":"Monitor audit output next week and decide further marketing initiatives based on results (42:10)","completed":false},{"text":"Verify Make (Integromat) operations usage with developers for potential subscription cost reduction (20:10)","completed":false},{"text":"Assist with HubSpot SMS automation setup, including workflow triggers and content, and create opted-out checkbox for text messaging compliance (26:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Lead paid ads audit for Meta platforms, deliver recommendations following December (36:30)","completed":false},{"text":"Support integration and access approvals for Facebook Business Manager (38:39)","completed":false},{"text":"Consult on website rebuild including HubSpot integration requirements and overall marketing strategy (47:30)","completed":false},{"text":"Provide tutorials and screenshot guides for workflows, lead gen forms, and manual enrollment in HubSpot (14:54)","completed":false},{"text":"Advise on email health metrics and HubSpot compliance monitoring (11:58)","completed":false},{"text":"Collaborate on the auditing and strategy implementation for SEO and website conversion improvement (48:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Support SMS automation setup and opt-out process alongside Colin and Milan (26:00)","completed":false}]'::jsonb,
