    1776,
    'https://us02web.zoom.us/j/83519004309?pwd=JvKSZR6BzSlyNxK5WTgZHYayMsLSKi.1&jst=2',
    '{"id":"01KC29T9M8EZY8HJFNNECE87XE","title":"KTC // MiD: Weekly Marketing Meeting","summary":{"notes":"## **Branding and Visual Identity**\n\nThe team decided to update the **KTC Search logo** to incorporate **Richie May''s green and blue colors** to align with the parent company''s branding and ease future integration (05:13).\n\n- **Michael Kersten** emphasized blending Richie May’s blue and green tones into the logo and website to create visual consistency with Richie May’s existing brands.\n- This change aims to support brand recognition as KTC Search builds its identity throughout **2026**, starting with no existing color recognition.\n- The updated colors will help position KTC Search as a standalone brand now but ready for smooth transition into Richie May’s ecosystem later.\n- The marketing team agreed to implement this immediately to leverage the current rebranding phase.\n\n## **Video Content and Marketing Strategy**\n\nKTC Search set up a **Riverside studio account** to start producing video content for the **Executive Advantage series**, aiming to launch initial videos by **January** and full client-featured videos by **May** (09:03).\n\n- **Michael Kersten** proposed using **Kristen Baller** as a surrogate spokesperson for video interviews until his availability after **May**, leveraging her prior experience with Dish to speed content creation.\n- This surrogate approach allows the company to start building video content early, maintaining momentum despite Michael’s limited camera availability.\n- The Riverside platform will support remote interviews and video testimonials, providing flexibility and professional quality.\n- Coordination meetings will be scheduled with Kristen to finalize scripting and interview prep, ensuring smooth content flow and alignment with marketing goals.\n\n## **Website Development and SEO**\n\nThe website redesign is progressing with rewritten SEO-optimized content and new designs incorporating the updated **green color scheme**, targeting a complete launch after development in **HubSpot** (12:27).\n\n- The team is rewriting content based on **search volume data** to improve organic discovery and lead generation.\n- The homepage and testimonial pages have been mocked up, with plans to add both text and video testimonials sourced from past clients.\n- Michael granted full creative autonomy to the marketing team to overhaul the site aggressively to compete effectively.\n- The website will be built and hosted in HubSpot, with a planned transition that includes domain forwarding from the current site after launch to avoid downtime.\n\n## **Client and Candidate Experience Pages**\n\nKTC Search will create specialized landing pages to highlight **sales organization building** and **utility manufacturer expertise**, reflecting Michael’s growing work in these sectors, as well as separate pages for **candidate experience** and **resume submissions** (15:53).\n\n- Michael is providing client and company details to tailor these pages around his core business strengths and client verticals, particularly in the utility space.\n- The candidate-focused pages will support resume intake and showcase testimonials to improve candidate engagement without posting open job roles.\n- The marketing team will integrate legal disclaimers and equal opportunity employer language only if needed, as no open job postings will be listed.\n- This differentiated approach ensures the site serves both clients and candidates effectively while maintaining compliance and brand clarity.\n\n## **Testimonial Acquisition and Client Engagement**\n\nMichael is leveraging strong relationships with key past clients, including an SVP at **Sunbudsalam** and a former RevOps SVP from **ID Me**, to secure video and written testimonials for the website and marketing materials (14:39).\n\n- These testimonials will be scripted and edited to focus on Michael’s value and services without revealing proprietary information or sensitive details.\n- The testimonial content will feed into the new testimonial page designs, helping build social proof and credibility with prospects.\n- The marketing team plans to provide Michael with guidelines and a content calendar to manage testimonial outreach efficiently.\n- These efforts aim to increase client trust and support lead generation through authentic endorsements.\n\n## **Operational Planning and Next Steps**\n\nThe team plans to maintain the current website live during development and then switch domain forwarding upon launch, ensuring a smooth transition with no loss of traffic or SEO ranking (27:01).\n\n- Hosting access and credentials have been requested to facilitate the migration and deployment process.\n- The next meeting is scheduled for **December 23rd**, with the team available to accommodate early morning meetings as needed to fit different time zones.\n- Kristen will be fully integrated into the marketing workflow as a key operational lead for video content and client coordination.\n- The marketing firm is positioned as a full **“soup to nuts”** marketing partner handling website, content, video, and HubSpot management to streamline KTC Search’s go-to-market efforts.","outline":null,"keywords":["Logo redesign","Riverside platform","Executive Advantage series","Website redesign","Client testimonials","Candidate experience"],"overview":"- **KTC Search Logo Update:** New logo will feature Richie May’s colors for brand consistency and recognition, starting 2026.  \n- **Video Content Production:** Riverside account established to launch Executive Advantage videos by January, utilizing Kristen as interim spokesperson.  \n- **Website Overhaul:** Redesign includes SEO-optimized content targeting organic leads, launching post-HubSpot development with domain transition planned.  \n- **Specialized Landing Pages:** New pages will highlight client expertise and improve candidate engagement, focusing on specific sectors without job postings.  \n- **Testimonial Strategy:** Client testimonials will enhance credibility on the website, with strict guidelines for sensitive information management.  \n- **Smooth Transition Planning:** Current website remains live during developments, with next meeting on December 23rd to discuss progress.","action_items":"\n**Colin Costigan**\nUpdate logo colors to integrate Richie May greens and blues per Michael’s guidance (05:20)\nShare Riverside platform credentials and usage instructions with Michael and Kristen (09:00)\nSchedule meeting with Kristen for interview/video process coordination (11:20)\nSend guidelines document and content calendar for testimonial interviews to Michael for client coordination (20:15)\nDevelop new website pages and candidate experience page in HubSpot including resume submission function (23:40)\nIncorporate legal disclaimers and privacy policy from existing site or create new page if needed (26:10)\nCoordinate transition plan for new website launch and domain forwarding with Ryan (27:00)\nProvide calendar link to Kristen for easy scheduling of future meetings (29:10)\n\n**Michael Kersten**\nProvide Richie May branding color references to Colin for logo revision (05:10)\nIntroduce Kristen Baller on call and share her email with Colin for coordination (17:00)\nFollow up with clients (e.g., ID.me and Sunbursalam) to secure testimonials and submit details to Colin (14:30)\nCoordinate with Ryan to ensure access and credentials provided to marketing team for website hosting and content updates (27:45)\n\n**Kristen Baller**\nCollaborate with Colin and Michael on content preps and interview scripting to serve as surrogate spokesperson (10:40)\nReview redesigned homepage and testimonial pages and provide feedback regarding staffing legal requirements and client/candidate experience sections (21:30)\n"},"duration":29.600000381469727,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Colin Costigan"},{"id":1,"name":"Michael Kersten"},{"id":2,"name":"Colin Costigan"},{"id":3,"name":"Kristen Baller"}],"sentences":[{"text":"Sa.","index":0,"end_time":128.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":127.89,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Guys.","index":1,"end_time":263.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":262.82,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Oh, how''s it going?","index":2,"end_time":264.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":263.7,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Good.","index":3,"end_time":265.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":264.82,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"How are you doing?","index":4,"end_time":266.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":265.1,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"All right.","index":5,"end_time":266.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":266.34,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You''re still in crazy busy season.","index":6,"end_time":269.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":266.9,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Oh, yeah.","index":7,"end_time":270.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":269.78,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Never stops down.","index":8,"end_time":273.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":270.58,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So it doesn''t look like I''m staring up at you guys.","index":9,"end_time":275.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":273.38,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"It''s on my other monitor, so no worries.","index":10,"end_time":278.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":275.7,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Well, busy is a good problem to have.","index":11,"end_time":281.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":280.1,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yep.","index":12,"end_time":282.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":282.17,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"All right, well, we got some exciting.","index":13,"end_time":286.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":284.97,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Stuff to walk through today.","index":14,"end_time":287.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":286.21,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Excellent.","index":15,"end_time":288.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":287.93,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"All right.","index":16,"end_time":291.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":290.41,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we have updated your.","index":17,"end_time":296.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":294.73,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Logo and wanted to show that to you.","index":18,"end_time":298.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":296.37,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''ve set up a Riverside account and we also have updates on the website.","index":19,"end_time":301.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":298.33,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Project and everything we''re doing there.","index":20,"end_time":303.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":301.77,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, so for the updated logo, here.","index":21,"end_time":307.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":303.69,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Are a few renderings of that.","index":22,"end_time":309.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":307.61,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":23,"end_time":310.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":309.73,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Any initial thoughts?","index":24,"end_time":312.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":311.33,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So let me ask you this.","index":25,"end_time":314.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":313.25,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Like it.","index":26,"end_time":316.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":315.41,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Is there any way we could get some of the Richie May colors into some of that anyway?","index":27,"end_time":321.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":316.53,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Some of the green?","index":28,"end_time":322.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":321.25,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, some of the green.","index":29,"end_time":323.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":322.37,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Just because I was talking to Felicia, the cmo.","index":30,"end_time":326.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":323.45,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So I was telling her how, you know, I''m using you guys to kind of do stuff in that.","index":31,"end_time":330.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":326.17,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"You know, obviously we were changing the colors to kind of match some of the Richie maybe.","index":32,"end_time":336.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":330.85,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And normally when we do is when we gobble up a company, if you go to the Richie May site and you hit their sites, you can see we''re just basically bringing their sites over.","index":33,"end_time":343.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":336.31,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So they have, you know, kind of necessary.","index":34,"end_time":346.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":344.23,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"They said if you go to.","index":35,"end_time":347.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":346.03,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Go to Richie May and then if you hit.","index":36,"end_time":350.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":348.63,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":37,"end_time":351.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":351.19,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Click on one of the offices, like who we are.","index":38,"end_time":353.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":351.67,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Let''s see.","index":39,"end_time":354.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":353.95,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Let''s see.","index":40,"end_time":355.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":354.55,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Locations go back to where.","index":41,"end_time":356.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":355.07,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yeah, go like click on Utah, for example.","index":42,"end_time":358.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":356.39,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"You can see it''s.","index":43,"end_time":361.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":360.15,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"What it''s doing is it''s kind of transitioning over.","index":44,"end_time":363.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":361.47,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"There''s.","index":45,"end_time":364.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":363.83,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"It''s typing their content and stuff like that.","index":46,"end_time":366.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":364.23,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So that was their logo and kind of bringing it.","index":47,"end_time":368.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":366.39,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So that''s ideally what we''ll probably do with our site.","index":48,"end_time":371.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":368.45,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"We''ll still stand as a standalone.","index":49,"end_time":374.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":372.69,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And just so you guys know and you can pass on your leadership, I''ve kind of said, hey, as I roll in, you know, if it''s first quarter, second quarter, you guys are going to be my marketing arm going forward.","index":50,"end_time":383.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":374.33,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And so she''s on board with all that, but she just asked if we change colors or marks, if we could.","index":51,"end_time":389.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":383.77,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"If we could get it closer to their stuff would be good.","index":52,"end_time":392.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":390.13,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Even if it''s using their blue like.","index":53,"end_time":394.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":392.49,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Like they have in the Richie May, the more that we could translate that, it kind of correlates with theirs less marked.","index":54,"end_time":400.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":394.17,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Because if you go.","index":55,"end_time":401.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":400.22,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Let me.","index":56,"end_time":403.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":402.7,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"We updated this deck here, let me show you, and I''ll send you this deck of Our.","index":57,"end_time":408.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":403.34,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Let me find it real quick and show you.","index":58,"end_time":410.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":408.62,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Sorry, I got too many damn monitors going here.","index":59,"end_time":412.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":410.42,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"One second here, Kristen.","index":60,"end_time":416.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":414.779,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Sorry.","index":61,"end_time":429.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":428.71,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Gonna find.","index":62,"end_time":430.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":429.51,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Get too many damn emails here.","index":63,"end_time":431.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":430.11,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"You guys see my screen?","index":64,"end_time":465.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":464.88,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yeah, I''m seeing the zoom.","index":65,"end_time":467.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":466.16,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Oh, the zoom.","index":66,"end_time":468.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":467.92,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Okay, hang on.","index":67,"end_time":469.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":468.68,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So that''s kind of the new.","index":68,"end_time":487.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":486.09,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"That''s when we just redid the deck a little bit, cleaning up some of the stuff on this that their.","index":69,"end_time":492.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":488.01,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Her PowerPoint person kind of did this.","index":70,"end_time":494.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":492.65,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"But you could kind of see the theme that they were kind of rolling there.","index":71,"end_time":498.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":494.73,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Once again, I don''t have to be exactly.","index":72,"end_time":501.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":499.93,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"But if we could roll in some of the Richie made colors so that way it doesn''t look like it''s totally different, that would deal.","index":73,"end_time":508.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":501.77,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, we can make that.","index":74,"end_time":510.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":508.94,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":75,"end_time":511.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":510.94,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I don''t.","index":76,"end_time":512.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":511.82,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Like I said, I don''t really.","index":77,"end_time":513.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":512.22,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"As you.","index":78,"end_time":513.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":513.14,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"You know, you guys will do a phenomenal job for me in 26.","index":79,"end_time":516.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":513.58,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So, you know, KTC will obviously have a, you know, a brand recognition hopefully by the end of 26.","index":80,"end_time":521.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":516.34,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"But right now nobody really knows my colors.","index":81,"end_time":524.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":521.94,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Nobody really knows anyhow.","index":82,"end_time":525.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":524.38,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So, you know, hey, if we throw some other stuff in there, nobody''s going to know any difference.","index":83,"end_time":529.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":525.66,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Any.","index":84,"end_time":529.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":529.1,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, now''s the time to do it.","index":85,"end_time":530.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":529.42,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s for sure.","index":86,"end_time":531.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":530.9,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, exactly.","index":87,"end_time":532.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":531.3,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Exactly.","index":88,"end_time":532.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":532.1,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":89,"end_time":533.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":533.34,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":90,"end_time":534.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":533.74,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, we can definitely make that change.","index":91,"end_time":535.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":534.1,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":92,"end_time":536.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":535.5,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Stop sharing.","index":93,"end_time":537.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":536.94,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So you can go back.","index":94,"end_time":538.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":537.62,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And then.","index":95,"end_time":543.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":543.34,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So another thing that we''ve set up, and I know that it''s not a time sensitive thing because.","index":96,"end_time":547.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":543.78,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Because of the situation that you have wrapping up at the end of Q1 next year, but we do have your Riverside set up and so we''ll send over those credentials.","index":97,"end_time":555.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":548.54,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Basically this operates as a.","index":98,"end_time":557.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":555.7,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Almost like a zoom.","index":99,"end_time":559.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":558.39,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You can just hop in and create a new studio and this is where any interviews or anything will be held.","index":100,"end_time":563.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":559.35,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So that we can get them into.","index":101,"end_time":564.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":563.91,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"The Executive Advantage series.","index":102,"end_time":566.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":564.91,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":103,"end_time":567.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":566.47,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So I have.","index":104,"end_time":567.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":567.07,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So we might be able to do stuff sooner.","index":105,"end_time":569.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":567.75,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Let me throw something by you guys and see if you''d be open to this.","index":106,"end_time":572.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":569.59,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So Kristen Baller, who is kind of.","index":107,"end_time":577.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":573.51,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I.","index":108,"end_time":578.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":577.95,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"She''s a contractor to me, but I''m gonna.","index":109,"end_time":580.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":578.39,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"But probably I''ll end up probably hiring her.","index":110,"end_time":582.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":580.15,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So I kind of have her acting as kind of a manager for me.","index":111,"end_time":587.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":582.71,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"She''s.","index":112,"end_time":588.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":587.61,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"If you look up her back, she worked at Dish for many years.","index":113,"end_time":590.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":588.37,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"You know, she''s.","index":114,"end_time":592.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":591.41,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"She''s been more on the ops.","index":115,"end_time":593.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":592.41,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I mean, yeah, she''s a recruiter, but I would say she''s better in regards to kind of the.","index":116,"end_time":597.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":593.61,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"The op side and bringing stuff together.","index":117,"end_time":599.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":597.97,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Well, long story short is A lot of what you guys are talking, we want to do, she did that stuff at Dish for the TA stuff.","index":118,"end_time":605.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":599.93,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So what I was thinking is, is if we have preps and stuff like that, I know you guys want to get me on camera, but for.","index":119,"end_time":611.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":606.29,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So we can maybe start getting stuff in January.","index":120,"end_time":613.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":611.89,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I was thinking about using her as a segregate, where you guys can give me the questions.","index":121,"end_time":618.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":614.41,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"She''s good on camera.","index":122,"end_time":620.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":619.21,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"She''s done all that for dish.","index":123,"end_time":621.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":620.41,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So she''ll be very showed, very photogenic and very good at it.","index":124,"end_time":624.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":621.57,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I was figuring is maybe we can use her as my surrogate.","index":125,"end_time":627.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":624.49,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"We come up with the questions, I provide her the data, and then you guys are interviewing her or whatever.","index":126,"end_time":631.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":627.13,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And then that way we can start getting some stuff up on the site sooner than later.","index":127,"end_time":636.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":631.81,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And once my shit happens, you know, by.","index":128,"end_time":639.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":636.57,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"You know, by the end of May, then we could, you know, we can start filming some stuff for me.","index":129,"end_time":643.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":639.05,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"But that way we''re not waiting to second quarter to get some video and stuff like that, because, I mean, she''s done that shit a lot.","index":130,"end_time":649.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":643.16,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"She''s really good at it.","index":131,"end_time":650.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":649.56,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And, you know, so if you guys don''t mind doing that, I''m totally.","index":132,"end_time":654.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":650.6,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Comforter is using her as a surrogate.","index":133,"end_time":656.839,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":654.84,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I''d have to give her the details, and then we script it out and she''s goes.","index":134,"end_time":660.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":656.92,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"But she''s been there, done that.","index":135,"end_time":662.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":660.68,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"She''s done it for dish, so, you know, she knew exactly what I was talking about when we were talking about.","index":136,"end_time":666.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":662.24,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So that''s something.","index":137,"end_time":667.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":666.36,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"If you guys would be open to that, I''d be, you know, from a company standpoint, I''m totally fine.","index":138,"end_time":672.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":667.4,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I don''t have to prom throwing her up on the website because she''s going to be part of the team anyhow, so.","index":139,"end_time":675.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":672.12,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yeah, absolutely.","index":140,"end_time":676.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":675.46,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Absolutely love that idea.","index":141,"end_time":678.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":676.66,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":142,"end_time":678.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":678.42,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So as far as next steps there, do you want to maybe should we have a meeting with her?","index":143,"end_time":683.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":679.94,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":144,"end_time":683.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":683.38,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Just talk about how this all goes.","index":145,"end_time":685.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":683.9,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":146,"end_time":685.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":685.02,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yep, yep, yep.","index":147,"end_time":685.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":685.26,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Definitely.","index":148,"end_time":686.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":685.98,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yep.","index":149,"end_time":686.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":686.38,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And then I''ll.","index":150,"end_time":688.899,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":686.74,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Let me put.","index":151,"end_time":689.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":688.9,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Let me see if I can keep going.","index":152,"end_time":696.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":691.94,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I can see if she can maybe even just join this call, and then you guys can coordinate with her.","index":153,"end_time":701.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":696.98,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Give me a second.","index":154,"end_time":701.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":701.1,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yeah, no problem.","index":155,"end_time":703.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":702.02,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Keep going.","index":156,"end_time":703.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":703.22,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Thanks again for moving too.","index":157,"end_time":713.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":712.18,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yeah, no problem.","index":158,"end_time":715.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":714.26,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I know you got a lot going on right now.","index":159,"end_time":717.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":715.78,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right, let''s see if she text back.","index":160,"end_time":731.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":730.19,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Go ahead.","index":161,"end_time":732.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":731.79,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":162,"end_time":733.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":732.67,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then so the only thing there is, we can set up the connection to Spotify.","index":163,"end_time":737.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":733.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"If you want to be listed on Apple, we.","index":164,"end_time":738.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":737.11,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We can send over instructions.","index":165,"end_time":740.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":738.79,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s just a lot easier for you to do it.","index":166,"end_time":741.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":740.03,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then instead of us dealing with like an icloud.","index":167,"end_time":743.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":741.79,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Icloud type situation.","index":168,"end_time":745.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":743.95,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we''ll send over.","index":169,"end_time":746.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":745.79,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yep.","index":170,"end_time":747.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":746.83,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":171,"end_time":748.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":747.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then so for the website, we''re making some good headway.","index":172,"end_time":751.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":748.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We have content that we''ve been rewriting, and so we''re picking out keywords based on the data that we''re seeing.","index":173,"end_time":756.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":751.03,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Search volume, rewriting the content.","index":174,"end_time":758.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":756.67,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we''ve done that for a few pages and we''ve also gotten into designing.","index":175,"end_time":764.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":760.05,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And so here is what we''ve designed for the homepage.","index":176,"end_time":767.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":764.65,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No, that looks great.","index":177,"end_time":769.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":768.29,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":178,"end_time":770.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":770.29,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So you can see we''re getting in some of the green.","index":179,"end_time":772.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":770.73,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yep.","index":180,"end_time":773.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":772.69,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"No, that''s awesome, guys.","index":181,"end_time":776.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":773.809,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Looking really good.","index":182,"end_time":777.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":776.45,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And then like I said, you guys, I know you''re going to do it anyhow, but you have full creativity.","index":183,"end_time":783.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":777.17,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I am not married any of that shit.","index":184,"end_time":785.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":783.69,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"If you blow up the whole damn thing and we burn more hours, I don''t care.","index":185,"end_time":788.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":785.21,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Do I want this to look like who we''re competing for?","index":186,"end_time":791.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":788.56,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And I think you guys get that.","index":187,"end_time":792.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":791.56,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So you guys have full autonomy to do whatever the hell you want.","index":188,"end_time":795.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":792.52,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yeah, love that.","index":189,"end_time":797.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":796.04,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And now.","index":190,"end_time":797.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":797.44,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And that that''s what we''re going for.","index":191,"end_time":799.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":797.96,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I feel like this is.","index":192,"end_time":801.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":800.28,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"This is hitting that point.","index":193,"end_time":802.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":801.28,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then we also have just a testimonial page here.","index":194,"end_time":807.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":802.36,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And we can definitely utilize when we have some.","index":195,"end_time":811.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":809,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"If we get some prospective clients or even past clients or anything onto those Riverside interviews, we can populate them here as well.","index":196,"end_time":818.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":811.16,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we have the oper opportunity to.","index":197,"end_time":820.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":818.92,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Do text or video testimonials on this page.","index":198,"end_time":822.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":820.3,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":199,"end_time":823.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":822.74,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And then I have.","index":200,"end_time":826.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":823.38,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And I need to talk to her because I know, like, if we have certain clients, there''s a handful of clients that I could, you know, once you guys tell me what you want is the rev ops v. SVP from ID me.","index":201,"end_time":837.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":826.98,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"They, you know, typical ID me, they ran her out the door the other day.","index":202,"end_time":840.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":837.94,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"But I have a real strong relationship with her.","index":203,"end_time":843.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":840.98,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Good working relationship.","index":204,"end_time":844.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":843.06,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"She would probably be somebody.","index":205,"end_time":846.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":844.82,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I could probably ask if she would mind doing a testimonial.","index":206,"end_time":850.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":846.22,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"You guys will have to wordsmith it because she''s going to talk about everything I did with her IB me.","index":207,"end_time":854.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":850.3,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So you guys would have to kind of, you know, script it a little bit differently, just so it doesn''t talk so much about that.","index":208,"end_time":860.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":854.56,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I can be kind of open and honest.","index":209,"end_time":862.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":860.64,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"She knows I have my own search business, but, you know, obviously I''m not going to, you know, let the cat out back that I was doing both at the same time, but she could obviously talk quite a bit about you know, what I''ve done and the services and uniqueness and working with me.","index":210,"end_time":876.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":862.04,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I think some of that''s the stuff that you guys are looking for anyhow, so.","index":211,"end_time":879.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":876.4,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":212,"end_time":879.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":879.44,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s absolutely perfect.","index":213,"end_time":880.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":879.8,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":214,"end_time":882.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":882.15,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And then, you know, like, some of like, I''m gonna.","index":215,"end_time":886.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":882.55,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I got a call on Friday with the SVP over at sunbudsalam, who I placed.","index":216,"end_time":890.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":886.07,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"He''s one of my candidates, and I''m doing a bunch of work for him.","index":217,"end_time":893.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":890.67,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So he''ll.","index":218,"end_time":894.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":893.55,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I''ll ask him when I talk to him on Friday if he''d be open to maybe just doing a testimony about working with me.","index":219,"end_time":898.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":894.03,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And, you know, he''s.","index":220,"end_time":899.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":898.27,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"He''s in the industry, so we could probably use him as a spokesperson, talk about what''s going on in the utility space, things like that.","index":221,"end_time":905.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":899.51,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"He''s a seasoned guy, real good guy, so I''m sure I can probably get him to do that too for us.","index":222,"end_time":910.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":905.47,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"This is music to my ears, Michael.","index":223,"end_time":912.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":911.09,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yep.","index":224,"end_time":913.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":912.85,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"This is awesome.","index":225,"end_time":914.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":913.81,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And that is actually everything that we had ready to go through today.","index":226,"end_time":919.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":915.01,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Usually people are a lot more like zoomed in and want to see every single grammatical point on these things.","index":227,"end_time":928.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":920.45,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"When are you guys.","index":228,"end_time":930.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":929.81,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"When are you guys looking to dump?","index":229,"end_time":932.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":930.85,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Or when are you guys bringing over, I guess, stuff into HubSpot?","index":230,"end_time":935.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":932.77,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I mean, you guys are.","index":231,"end_time":936.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":935.65,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Got access into my housewives.","index":232,"end_time":937.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":936.41,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I think you guys are in there.","index":233,"end_time":938.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":937.61,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yep.","index":234,"end_time":939.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":938.96,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So are we building these pages and stuff in there and right into it then?","index":235,"end_time":942.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":939.32,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yep.","index":236,"end_time":943.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":942.64,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":237,"end_time":944.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":943.28,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":238,"end_time":944.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":944.32,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So once.","index":239,"end_time":946,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":944.76,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Once all the pages are designed and written out, then we''ll just go into full development mode and then we get the website launched and connect to your domain and everything like that.","index":240,"end_time":953.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":946,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, now the other question I had, just because one of the things that we had talked about since I''m doing a lot of work in that and Kristen should be joining here shortly, but can you guys.","index":241,"end_time":962.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":953.4,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And maybe it''s a separate landing page that we do when you start marketing out to clients, but I would like to highlight on my site, you know, when it comes to talking about building out sales organizations, maybe a specialized page for that, but then also kind of doing a specialized page, really kind of highlighting all the work that I''m doing for utility manufacturers.","index":242,"end_time":982.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":962.12,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I mean, I can give you some of the companies that I''m working with, you can see, but kind of in that utility space, because Oaktree, which is, you know, one of my PE clients, they''re just loading me up with a lot of their portfolio companies over the last couple days.","index":243,"end_time":995.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":982.95,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"They''ve been dumping us, so.","index":244,"end_time":997.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":995.71,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And I''ve done the last 18 months.","index":245,"end_time":999.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":997.62,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"That''s a lot of where my retained stuff has been.","index":246,"end_time":1002.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":999.94,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So that would be huge to maybe highlight, that is because I know when you guys go to market, we were going to kind of hit different types of stuff when we started those campaigns and things like that.","index":247,"end_time":1011.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1002.9,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So, you know, I think, and I don''t thought that''s a separate landing page or whatever, however you guys want to develop.","index":248,"end_time":1016.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1011.78,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"But those are two areas that I think we want to make sure we highlight because I have a lot of experience in that type of stuff.","index":249,"end_time":1021.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1016.1,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So.","index":250,"end_time":1022.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1021.86,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":251,"end_time":1022.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1022.14,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s amazing.","index":252,"end_time":1023.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1022.46,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And any info you have, please send it over.","index":253,"end_time":1024.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1023.14,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I will say we were already kind of planning on having content dedicated to that as well.","index":254,"end_time":1029.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1025.46,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":255,"end_time":1030.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1030.04,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":256,"end_time":1031.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1031,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So glad that we''re aligned there.","index":257,"end_time":1032.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1031.56,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And Hi, Kristen.","index":258,"end_time":1033.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1032.96,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Great to meet you.","index":259,"end_time":1034.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1033.6,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So, hey, Kristen, I signed you up.","index":260,"end_time":1037.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1035.72,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So.","index":261,"end_time":1037.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1037.4,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So these guys are the marketing firm that I''m using.","index":262,"end_time":1041.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1037.88,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"They''re kind of taking over.","index":263,"end_time":1042.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1041.48,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"They''re redoing the website.","index":264,"end_time":1044.199,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1043,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"We''re making changes, modification the website.","index":265,"end_time":1046.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1044.2,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"They''ll do all our content, but they, they also want to, they do a lot of the video.","index":266,"end_time":1050.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1046.36,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So for kind of the, some of the interviewing clients, speaking engagements.","index":267,"end_time":1054.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1050.12,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And I told them that you are a spokesperson since you did that all at dish, so they wanted to set up some time with you to kind of do so since I''m kind of, I can''t be on, on the website at least until after May.","index":268,"end_time":1066.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1054.78,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I''m sorry, after March.","index":269,"end_time":1068.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1066.98,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"But I didn''t want to wait that long for stuff.","index":270,"end_time":1070.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1068.86,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And I said since you did that, you kindly volunteered to be the spokesperson and go on camera.","index":271,"end_time":1076.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1070.74,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So they wanted to talk to you.","index":272,"end_time":1077.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1076.18,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So I''ll shut up and let them talk.","index":273,"end_time":1078.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1077.34,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":274,"end_time":1080.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1080.39,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Great to meet you, Kristen.","index":275,"end_time":1081.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1080.59,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You as well.","index":276,"end_time":1082.55,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1081.83,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"So when you were doing things at Dish, were you using any specific platforms for recording?","index":277,"end_time":1089.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1083.51,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So a lot of the speaking engagements that I was doing at Dish were external speaking engagement.","index":278,"end_time":1095.47,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1090.39,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"So I was either doing virtual conferences or I was being sent to go do other types of conferences.","index":279,"end_time":1102.39,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1095.47,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"And I did that both in conjunction.","index":280,"end_time":1104.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1102.39,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"I oversaw our employer brand and so I did that in conjunction with employer brand and then in partnership with our PR team and really more so like around when we, we were going through acquisitions and we are publicly traded company and so there was just some other small pieces.","index":281,"end_time":1125.74,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1104.15,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"So platforms, I.","index":282,"end_time":1129.9,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1126.78,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"They all feel, they all felt relatively the same.","index":283,"end_time":1133.9,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1130.62,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":284,"end_time":1134.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1134.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So but I couldn''t name them off the back of my hand right now.","index":285,"end_time":1138.83,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1135.83,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"If you, if you go back and look.","index":286,"end_time":1141.35,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1138.83,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"Yeah, no worries.","index":287,"end_time":1142.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1141.35,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So the platform that we use because we have a partnership set up with them Is Riverside okay?","index":288,"end_time":1147.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1142.63,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Have you used that before?","index":289,"end_time":1148.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1147.83,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yes.","index":290,"end_time":1149.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1149.03,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":291,"end_time":1150.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1149.75,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So it''s.","index":292,"end_time":1150.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1150.35,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, nice and easy.","index":293,"end_time":1151.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1150.75,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s just like hopping on a zoom call.","index":294,"end_time":1152.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1151.55,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And so we already have the studio set up.","index":295,"end_time":1155.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1153.35,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We can send you all of the information from the content plan that we wrote.","index":296,"end_time":1158.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1155.75,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"The series is called the Executive Advantage series, and it''s really rooted in a couple different themes of interviewing past clients that have worked with Kirsten, you know, future prospects, businesses that he has placed candidates at, or even just solo interview videos where we have a series of questions.","index":297,"end_time":1180.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1159.67,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And it''s just kind of based on industry trends.","index":298,"end_time":1182.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1180.37,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":299,"end_time":1183.65,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1183.09,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"Okay.","index":300,"end_time":1184.45,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1183.89,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"And sorry, what was the series name again?","index":301,"end_time":1186.29,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1184.53,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"The Executive Advantage series.","index":302,"end_time":1188.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1186.45,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":303,"end_time":1188.93,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1188.29,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"So everything''s already all designed out for that.","index":304,"end_time":1194.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1192.78,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then, hey, Colin, as I''m talking to Darren on Friday, and then I talked to AJ if you guys can kind of give me kind of some general ideas of what you''re thinking for.","index":305,"end_time":1205.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1195.34,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And these would be clients that I''ve worked with just so I can say, hey, here''s what you''re.","index":306,"end_time":1209.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1205.7,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"How much time I need from you, and here''s some of the stuff that we would do so I can kind of let them know what they''re signing up for too.","index":307,"end_time":1215.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1209.5,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"That help?","index":308,"end_time":1216.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1215.58,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":309,"end_time":1216.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1216.3,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So what we can do is oftentimes we''ll produce like a guidelines document and that''s just something you can send off to them.","index":310,"end_time":1222.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1216.66,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then we can also create like a content calendar.","index":311,"end_time":1225.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1223.17,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":312,"end_time":1225.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1225.25,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":313,"end_time":1226.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1225.97,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":314,"end_time":1228.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1227.81,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And then, hey, can you bring up some of those different pages again, Kristen?","index":315,"end_time":1232.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1229.01,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Here''s some of the stuff that they''re changing if you want to see.","index":316,"end_time":1234.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1232.01,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So here is a redesign of the.","index":317,"end_time":1239.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1237.81,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Homepage with some updated content as well.","index":318,"end_time":1242.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1239.93,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":319,"end_time":1245.57,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1244.93,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"And are you all just responsible for the redesign?","index":320,"end_time":1254.22,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1250.86,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"I noticed that There were some 404 errors that are currently coming through.","index":321,"end_time":1258.06,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1254.22,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"Are you auditing that?","index":322,"end_time":1259.34,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1258.06,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"Are they auditing?","index":323,"end_time":1260.38,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1259.5,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"We are not managing the current website.","index":324,"end_time":1261.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1260.38,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s the old.","index":325,"end_time":1263.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1262.46,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"That''s the old site.","index":326,"end_time":1263.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1263.14,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yep.","index":327,"end_time":1264.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1263.94,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"That''s okay.","index":328,"end_time":1265.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1264.22,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yep.","index":329,"end_time":1265.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1265.22,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"They''re redoing everything.","index":330,"end_time":1266.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1265.58,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So they''re.","index":331,"end_time":1266.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1266.42,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"They''re soup to nuts.","index":332,"end_time":1267.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1266.9,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So they''re web content digital.","index":333,"end_time":1270.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1267.94,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"They''re four firms into one.","index":334,"end_time":1272.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1271.02,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So they provide the whole, what I''d call the whole go gtm, go to market scheme.","index":335,"end_time":1276.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1272.7,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So they''re doing it all.","index":336,"end_time":1277.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1276.58,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And then they''ll also handle all of our landing pages, everything in HubSpot and everything else.","index":337,"end_time":1283.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1277.5,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So there''s.","index":338,"end_time":1284.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1283.81,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Think of them as soup to nuts.","index":339,"end_time":1285.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1284.25,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Whole marketing team in one.","index":340,"end_time":1287.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1286.41,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Got it.","index":341,"end_time":1288.97,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1288.33,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"Great.","index":342,"end_time":1295.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1294.97,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Oh, hey, on the, on that page right there where it says talk to Michael, can we modify that to say, hey, talk to KTC or something like that.","index":343,"end_time":1310.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1302.65,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Just so it''s not calling me out once again, don''t want to make it look like we''re just individual.","index":344,"end_time":1313.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1310.21,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yep, yep.","index":345,"end_time":1314.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1313.11,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And then what they''re going to do is as they, the color palettes, they''re, they''ll, they''re going to blend in some of the Richie May colors because eventually when that tr.","index":346,"end_time":1333.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1323.75,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"When we transition into that, is this another business unit will go to their master page.","index":347,"end_time":1339.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1333.47,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"But then, you know, our color scheme isn''t totally different from what they''re doing.","index":348,"end_time":1342.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1339.05,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So they''re, they are blending in some of the Richie Mae color schemes.","index":349,"end_time":1345.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1342.81,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Okay, can you, Sorry, can you go back up to the top?","index":350,"end_time":1349.61,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1346.49,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":351,"end_time":1350.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1350.09,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Now, Michael, is this only client facing or is this going to be.","index":352,"end_time":1355.37,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1351.53,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"If a candidate went to the.","index":353,"end_time":1358.65,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1356.17,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"This is all external facing, so this is our client.","index":354,"end_time":1362.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1359.77,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So if a customer went to that or a candidate went to this, they would see that too.","index":355,"end_time":1366.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1362.41,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"But I don''t the way we''ve had.","index":356,"end_time":1368.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1366.09,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"If they were going to apply to a role or anything like that.","index":357,"end_time":1371.23,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1369.03,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"Oh, I don''t, I don''t post any of our roles up on the site just because of the level we do.","index":358,"end_time":1374.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1371.23,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So I don''t, I don''t really have a.","index":359,"end_time":1376.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1374.95,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"We have, I think something on the current thing.","index":360,"end_time":1378.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1376.95,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"If somebody wants to submit their resume or something like that, they can do that kind of.","index":361,"end_time":1382.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1378.59,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"That may be something you guys want to look at, maybe how Korn and some of them do it.","index":362,"end_time":1385.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1382.23,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Maybe we throw up separate pages from a candid experience.","index":363,"end_time":1387.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1385.23,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"But from the purpose of the site, I''m not, I''m not, I don''t post any of our roles out there.","index":364,"end_time":1393.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1387.83,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So it''s more for client experience.","index":365,"end_time":1396.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1393.59,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Client view.","index":366,"end_time":1397.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1396.51,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"The necessary candid experience.","index":367,"end_time":1398.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1397.23,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":368,"end_time":1399.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1399.55,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And if we want a page that''s dedicated to the, the candidates experience of working with KTC Search, we can build that out and we can also add.","index":369,"end_time":1408.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1399.95,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"In very easily a function for them to give you their resume.","index":370,"end_time":1410.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1408.39,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":371,"end_time":1411.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1411.07,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Let''s, let''s throw that as maybe as another thing because like I said, there''s a lot.","index":372,"end_time":1415.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1411.71,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"If you go to my personal site, there''s a lot of testimony about what people worked with and a lot of the candidates that people I would hook you guys up with are people I placed anyhow.","index":373,"end_time":1423.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1415.07,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So just so we''re consistent with probably the big five, that''s probably something we should do.","index":374,"end_time":1430.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1423.71,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I mean, it could be towards on the back side of it, but, you know, that''s probably a good point.","index":375,"end_time":1434.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1430.1,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So.","index":376,"end_time":1434.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1434.02,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s great.","index":377,"end_time":1437.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1434.38,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then, Kristen, this is another page that we just have mocked up for showing testimonials.","index":378,"end_time":1441.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1437.78,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Be able to do video or text testimonials as well.","index":379,"end_time":1444.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1441.94,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":380,"end_time":1445.74,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1445.18,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"So, yeah, we''re going through redrafting all the content, updating it for SEO purposes.","index":381,"end_time":1453.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1448.78,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then redesigning and then we''ll develop it all in HubSpot.","index":382,"end_time":1456.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1453.42,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We have client testimonies.","index":383,"end_time":1461.19,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1459.87,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"Do you want to add any, Michael, Any placed, like individuals that were placed testimonies?","index":384,"end_time":1470.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1461.19,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"Maybe somebody from the C suite or somebody talking.","index":385,"end_time":1473.47,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1470.15,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"Right.","index":386,"end_time":1474.35,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1473.95,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"It wasn''t a process because, like it wasn''t me applying.","index":387,"end_time":1478.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1474.35,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"Right.","index":388,"end_time":1478.43,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1478.15,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"It was the seamless pro.","index":389,"end_time":1479.87,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1478.43,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"Their, their experience.","index":390,"end_time":1480.83,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1479.87,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"Yeah, they''re going to get those through when we, when I hook them up with testimonials that''ll come from the testimonies that they''re gonna, they''re gonna reproduce all that stuff for us.","index":391,"end_time":1489.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1481.8,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yep.","index":392,"end_time":1489.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1489.12,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Okay.","index":393,"end_time":1490.16,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1489.64,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"And then, Colin, just this is my last question.","index":394,"end_time":1492.6,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1490.16,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"Have you guys, have you supported staffing agents or staffing organizations like this before?","index":395,"end_time":1501.24,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1493.56,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":396,"end_time":1502.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1501.64,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean, we work with.","index":397,"end_time":1503.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1502.52,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, we handle almost anything in B2B.","index":398,"end_time":1507.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1504.28,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":399,"end_time":1508.67,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1508.27,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"I asked because I''m wondering where on the website do we need to put that?","index":400,"end_time":1513.07,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1509.15,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"Even though we''re not asking for individuals to apply and I''m sorry, I''m just.","index":401,"end_time":1517.63,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1513.07,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"I''ve got a small screen and a big screen.","index":402,"end_time":1519.39,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1517.63,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"I promise I''m looking at you when we''re asking individuals.","index":403,"end_time":1523.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1519.87,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"But when we''re talking about staffing or how do we include some of the legal.","index":404,"end_time":1529.11,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1523.31,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"Legalities, the language around.","index":405,"end_time":1530.83,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1529.11,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"We''re an equal opportunity employer.","index":406,"end_time":1533.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1530.91,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"There''s stuff depending on Michael, where.","index":407,"end_time":1537.17,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1534.25,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"Are you ready?","index":408,"end_time":1537.73,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1537.17,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"If Michael.","index":409,"end_time":1538.33,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1537.73,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"If Kirsten is registered in Colorado, there''s additional stuff that we need to just add in the footnote of the website.","index":410,"end_time":1544.41,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1538.33,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"I think that''s only if we''re posting.","index":411,"end_time":1547.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1546.17,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Some of that is just from a posting.","index":412,"end_time":1549.369,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1547.89,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"We''re not posting positions.","index":413,"end_time":1550.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1549.369,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So some of that.","index":414,"end_time":1551.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1550.73,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Some of that stuff doesn''t flow.","index":415,"end_time":1552.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1551.49,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I think we have.","index":416,"end_time":1553.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1552.65,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"If you go on our current page where it talks about disclaimers or some of that.","index":417,"end_time":1558.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1553.45,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"That.","index":418,"end_time":1558.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1558.61,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I think some of that''s on there.","index":419,"end_time":1560.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1558.93,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So they''ll, they''ll bring that over.","index":420,"end_time":1562.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1560.29,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"But since I don''t like typical corporate sites, you''re posting wrecks and stuff like that, we''re not doing that.","index":421,"end_time":1569.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1562.73,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So some of that legality I won''t have to worry about in individual states because I''m not posting jobs.","index":422,"end_time":1575.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1569.41,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So.","index":423,"end_time":1575.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1575.61,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":424,"end_time":1577.93,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1577.45,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":425,"end_time":1579.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1578.97,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And if ever we needed any disclaimers, we would create an additional page for.","index":426,"end_time":1582.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1579.33,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That and link to it in the footer.","index":427,"end_time":1583.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1582.09,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":428,"end_time":1583.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1583.45,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":429,"end_time":1584.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1583.93,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Take a look at.","index":430,"end_time":1585.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1584.29,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I know when I had a register with some of the, like my SMS messaging and Some of that.","index":431,"end_time":1592.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1585.21,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I had Ryan throw some of that on there.","index":432,"end_time":1594.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1592.39,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So if you guys look at my current site, I think there''s a disclaimer page or something.","index":433,"end_time":1598.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1594.35,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I think that was with the minimum stuff that I needed because I know like when I got like ring central and a few of those things when I was doing texting functions, I had to have some on my website so they would approve me.","index":434,"end_time":1608.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1598.15,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So.","index":435,"end_time":1608.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1608.43,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":436,"end_time":1609.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1608.95,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":437,"end_time":1609.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1609.35,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s typically around the privacy policy.","index":438,"end_time":1611.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1609.59,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":439,"end_time":1613.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1612.87,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Pretty boilerplate.","index":440,"end_time":1614.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1613.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yep.","index":441,"end_time":1614.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1614.26,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Exactly.","index":442,"end_time":1615.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1614.62,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yep.","index":443,"end_time":1615.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1615.14,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":444,"end_time":1617.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1616.98,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Cool.","index":445,"end_time":1618.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1617.86,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"All right.","index":446,"end_time":1619.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1618.58,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"All right.","index":447,"end_time":1619.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1619.06,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Exciting stuff coming along.","index":448,"end_time":1620.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1619.54,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right, sounds good.","index":449,"end_time":1622.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1621.14,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Are you guys the next couple?","index":450,"end_time":1625.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1623.7,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I know when it.","index":451,"end_time":1625.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1625.02,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Oh, winner.","index":452,"end_time":1626.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1625.7,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"When are you guys.","index":453,"end_time":1627.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1626.46,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"When do I need to cut Ryan loose?","index":454,"end_time":1630.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1628.74,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Do you guys.","index":455,"end_time":1631.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1630.66,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"What''s your kind of plan in regards when we start?","index":456,"end_time":1633.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1631.22,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Because I''m assuming we''ll leave that side up and then you''re going to move it and we''ll just decide a certain day.","index":457,"end_time":1636.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1633.14,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"We''re switch.","index":458,"end_time":1637.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1636.82,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"We''re cutting over to the new one, right?","index":459,"end_time":1638.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1637.34,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":460,"end_time":1639.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1638.98,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So what, what I would recommend is having the KTC Search like site go live and then, and then we tell Ryan to just forward the Kirsten Talent Capital domain to KTC Search and just.","index":461,"end_time":1650.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1639.46,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Take down his website.","index":462,"end_time":1651.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1650.3,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay cool.","index":463,"end_time":1652.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1651.54,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":464,"end_time":1652.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1652.18,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Okay cool.","index":465,"end_time":1652.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1652.5,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And I think you guys, I think he sent sent you guys all the credentials into that site.","index":466,"end_time":1657.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1652.94,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So you guys should have access to that.","index":467,"end_time":1659.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1657.94,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"But if not, email him copy me, he''ll give you access.","index":468,"end_time":1662.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1659.66,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I told him to give you guys whatever access you needed, so.","index":469,"end_time":1665.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1662.86,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Okay, perfect.","index":470,"end_time":1665.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1665.3,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right, I''ll check for that.","index":471,"end_time":1666.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1665.94,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s typically hosting that we would need access to.","index":472,"end_time":1669.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1666.78,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I''ll just check in on that.","index":473,"end_time":1670.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1669.26,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":474,"end_time":1671.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1670.51,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":475,"end_time":1671.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1671.03,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":476,"end_time":1671.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1671.51,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right, sounds good.","index":477,"end_time":1672.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1671.87,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And then did you guys.","index":478,"end_time":1673.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1672.63,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Do we need to meet?","index":479,"end_time":1674.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1673.59,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Are we meeting?","index":480,"end_time":1674.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1674.35,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I know we got holiday next week.","index":481,"end_time":1676.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1675.07,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So when did you guys want to meet again?","index":482,"end_time":1677.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1676.39,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So I didn''t know if you''re taking time off so.","index":483,"end_time":1679.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1677.79,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So we are closed on the 25th and the 1st.","index":484,"end_time":1683.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1680.35,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we can still hold our, our meeting on the 23rd.","index":485,"end_time":1687.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1684.75,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, unless.","index":486,"end_time":1688.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1687.47,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay cool.","index":487,"end_time":1689.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1688.47,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No, that''s fine.","index":488,"end_time":1689.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1689.15,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"It''s only up to you guys.","index":489,"end_time":1690.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1689.79,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yep.","index":490,"end_time":1690.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1690.51,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So if you guys got work, we''d definitely meet.","index":491,"end_time":1692.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1690.83,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So yeah, it''s been like kind of a 5050 split for me of clients just canceling.","index":492,"end_time":1695.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1692.31,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No.","index":493,"end_time":1696.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1696.26,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Versus yeah, still not.","index":494,"end_time":1697.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1696.42,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I''m totally, I''m totally fine.","index":495,"end_time":1698.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1697.66,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So whatever''s easier for you.","index":496,"end_time":1699.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1698.94,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"And if I need to go earlier or later, I mean I''m early riser.","index":497,"end_time":1703.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1699.94,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"So if I don''t know if you guys are east coast where you guys sit but I mean if since it''s right before the holiday if you guys need me to go earlier.","index":498,"end_time":1708.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1703.5,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"I start going about 5am so whatever time you guys want to roll, just let me know.","index":499,"end_time":1712.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1709.22,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Nice.","index":500,"end_time":1713.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1712.98,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I''m in Maryland and Guille is in Mexico.","index":501,"end_time":1716.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1713.42,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, nice, nice.","index":502,"end_time":1718.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1716.9,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Starts at 5am he never stops, so.","index":503,"end_time":1721.7,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1719.54,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"Yeah, he starts at 5am and he stops at 4:15.","index":504,"end_time":1724.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1722.42,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":505,"end_time":1728.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1728.24,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right.","index":506,"end_time":1728.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1728.56,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Well, Michael, great to see you as always.","index":507,"end_time":1730,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1728.84,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Kristen, it was fantastic to meet you as well.","index":508,"end_time":1731.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1730,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yep.","index":509,"end_time":1732.56,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1732,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"I am just for availability you whenever needing to schedule something if you want to in your outreach, you can provide times immediately.","index":510,"end_time":1741.8,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1732.8,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"And if I can move things around, I''ll move it around to accommodate so that we''re not stuck in a loop of trying to get.","index":511,"end_time":1748.16,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1741.8,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"Get things.","index":512,"end_time":1748.88,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1748.32,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"Yeah, we just.","index":513,"end_time":1749.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1748.88,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''ll send over.","index":514,"end_time":1750.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1749.52,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I send over a link that has my calendar and you can just book anytime that works for you.","index":515,"end_time":1753.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1750.2,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Sounds good.","index":516,"end_time":1754.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1754,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But yeah, that being said, Michael, if you could just send me Kristen''s email address, that''d be right now.","index":517,"end_time":1760.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1754.52,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Thanks.","index":518,"end_time":1761.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1760.8,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"All right, thank you, guys.","index":519,"end_time":1762.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1761.44,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Thanks.","index":520,"end_time":1762.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1762.56,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Sounds good.","index":521,"end_time":1763.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1762.96,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Bye.","index":522,"end_time":1764.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1763.68,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Kristen, you''re still good at top down, right?","index":523,"end_time":1765.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1764.08,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":524,"end_time":1766.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1766.08,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''m just going to refill my water bottle.","index":525,"end_time":1768.12,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1766.48,"speaker_name":"Kristen Baller"},{"text":"All right, cool.","index":526,"end_time":1768.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1768.12,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Talk to you a bit.","index":527,"end_time":1769.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1768.64,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"},{"text":"Bye.","index":528,"end_time":1769.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1769.16,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Thanks.","index":529,"end_time":1769.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1769.56,"speaker_name":"Michael Kersten"}],"dateString":"2025-12-16T18:30:00.000Z","host_email":"colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com","meeting_link":"https://us02web.zoom.us/j/83519004309?pwd=JvKSZR6BzSlyNxK5WTgZHYayMsLSKi.1&jst=2","participants":["colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com,guille.santana@marketersindemand.com,michael@kerstentalentcapital.com","guille.santana@marketersindemand.com","michael@kerstentalentcapital.com"],"transcript_url":"https://app.fireflies.ai/view/01KC29T9M8EZY8HJFNNECE87XE","organizer_email":"colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com"}'::jsonb,
    '{"label":"positive","confidence":0.93,"bullets":["Delivered redesigned homepage and logo mockups; Michael approved direction and encouraged full creative freedom.","Proposed using Kristen Baller as spokesperson to accelerate video content rollout before Q2 availability.","Confirmed HubSpot will be used for full site development and CRM content integration post-design.","Michael requested dedicated landing pages on sales hiring and utility work to support new client growth.","Planned testimonial content from clients and candidates; Michael securing approvals and script coordination."],"highlights":[{"quote":"You guys have full autonomy to do whatever the hell you want.","speaker":"Michael Kersten"},{"quote":"I am totally fine using her as a surrogate... she''s really good at it.","speaker":"Michael Kersten"},{"quote":"We''re making some good headway. We have content that we''ve been rewriting.","speaker":"Colin Costigan"}],"topics":["branding","video","testimonials","delivery","alignment"],"model":"openai/gpt-4-1106-preview","version":1,"generated_at":"2025-12-16T00:00:00Z"}'::jsonb,
    '{"fireflies_summary":{"notes":"## **Branding and Visual Identity**\n\nThe team decided to update the **KTC Search logo** to incorporate **Richie May''s green and blue colors** to align with the parent company''s branding and ease future integration (05:13).\n\n- **Michael Kersten** emphasized blending Richie May’s blue and green tones into the logo and website to create visual consistency with Richie May’s existing brands.\n- This change aims to support brand recognition as KTC Search builds its identity throughout **2026**, starting with no existing color recognition.\n- The updated colors will help position KTC Search as a standalone brand now but ready for smooth transition into Richie May’s ecosystem later.\n- The marketing team agreed to implement this immediately to leverage the current rebranding phase.\n\n## **Video Content and Marketing Strategy**\n\nKTC Search set up a **Riverside studio account** to start producing video content for the **Executive Advantage series**, aiming to launch initial videos by **January** and full client-featured videos by **May** (09:03).\n\n- **Michael Kersten** proposed using **Kristen Baller** as a surrogate spokesperson for video interviews until his availability after **May**, leveraging her prior experience with Dish to speed content creation.\n- This surrogate approach allows the company to start building video content early, maintaining momentum despite Michael’s limited camera availability.\n- The Riverside platform will support remote interviews and video testimonials, providing flexibility and professional quality.\n- Coordination meetings will be scheduled with Kristen to finalize scripting and interview prep, ensuring smooth content flow and alignment with marketing goals.\n\n## **Website Development and SEO**\n\nThe website redesign is progressing with rewritten SEO-optimized content and new designs incorporating the updated **green color scheme**, targeting a complete launch after development in **HubSpot** (12:27).\n\n- The team is rewriting content based on **search volume data** to improve organic discovery and lead generation.\n- The homepage and testimonial pages have been mocked up, with plans to add both text and video testimonials sourced from past clients.\n- Michael granted full creative autonomy to the marketing team to overhaul the site aggressively to compete effectively.\n- The website will be built and hosted in HubSpot, with a planned transition that includes domain forwarding from the current site after launch to avoid downtime.\n\n## **Client and Candidate Experience Pages**\n\nKTC Search will create specialized landing pages to highlight **sales organization building** and **utility manufacturer expertise**, reflecting Michael’s growing work in these sectors, as well as separate pages for **candidate experience** and **resume submissions** (15:53).\n\n- Michael is providing client and company details to tailor these pages around his core business strengths and client verticals, particularly in the utility space.\n- The candidate-focused pages will support resume intake and showcase testimonials to improve candidate engagement without posting open job roles.\n- The marketing team will integrate legal disclaimers and equal opportunity employer language only if needed, as no open job postings will be listed.\n- This differentiated approach ensures the site serves both clients and candidates effectively while maintaining compliance and brand clarity.\n\n## **Testimonial Acquisition and Client Engagement**\n\nMichael is leveraging strong relationships with key past clients, including an SVP at **Sunbudsalam** and a former RevOps SVP from **ID Me**, to secure video and written testimonials for the website and marketing materials (14:39).\n\n- These testimonials will be scripted and edited to focus on Michael’s value and services without revealing proprietary information or sensitive details.\n- The testimonial content will feed into the new testimonial page designs, helping build social proof and credibility with prospects.\n- The marketing team plans to provide Michael with guidelines and a content calendar to manage testimonial outreach efficiently.\n- These efforts aim to increase client trust and support lead generation through authentic endorsements.\n\n## **Operational Planning and Next Steps**\n\nThe team plans to maintain the current website live during development and then switch domain forwarding upon launch, ensuring a smooth transition with no loss of traffic or SEO ranking (27:01).\n\n- Hosting access and credentials have been requested to facilitate the migration and deployment process.\n- The next meeting is scheduled for **December 23rd**, with the team available to accommodate early morning meetings as needed to fit different time zones.\n- Kristen will be fully integrated into the marketing workflow as a key operational lead for video content and client coordination.\n- The marketing firm is positioned as a full **“soup to nuts”** marketing partner handling website, content, video, and HubSpot management to streamline KTC Search’s go-to-market efforts.","outline":null,"keywords":["Logo redesign","Riverside platform","Executive Advantage series","Website redesign","Client testimonials","Candidate experience"],"overview":"- **KTC Search Logo Update:** New logo will feature Richie May’s colors for brand consistency and recognition, starting 2026.  \n- **Video Content Production:** Riverside account established to launch Executive Advantage videos by January, utilizing Kristen as interim spokesperson.  \n- **Website Overhaul:** Redesign includes SEO-optimized content targeting organic leads, launching post-HubSpot development with domain transition planned.  \n- **Specialized Landing Pages:** New pages will highlight client expertise and improve candidate engagement, focusing on specific sectors without job postings.  \n- **Testimonial Strategy:** Client testimonials will enhance credibility on the website, with strict guidelines for sensitive information management.  \n- **Smooth Transition Planning:** Current website remains live during developments, with next meeting on December 23rd to discuss progress.","action_items":"\n**Colin Costigan**\nUpdate logo colors to integrate Richie May greens and blues per Michael’s guidance (05:20)\nShare Riverside platform credentials and usage instructions with Michael and Kristen (09:00)\nSchedule meeting with Kristen for interview/video process coordination (11:20)\nSend guidelines document and content calendar for testimonial interviews to Michael for client coordination (20:15)\nDevelop new website pages and candidate experience page in HubSpot including resume submission function (23:40)\nIncorporate legal disclaimers and privacy policy from existing site or create new page if needed (26:10)\nCoordinate transition plan for new website launch and domain forwarding with Ryan (27:00)\nProvide calendar link to Kristen for easy scheduling of future meetings (29:10)\n\n**Michael Kersten**\nProvide Richie May branding color references to Colin for logo revision (05:10)\nIntroduce Kristen Baller on call and share her email with Colin for coordination (17:00)\nFollow up with clients (e.g., ID.me and Sunbursalam) to secure testimonials and submit details to Colin (14:30)\nCoordinate with Ryan to ensure access and credentials provided to marketing team for website hosting and content updates (27:45)\n\n**Kristen Baller**\nCollaborate with Colin and Michael on content preps and interview scripting to serve as surrogate spokesperson (10:40)\nReview redesigned homepage and testimonial pages and provide feedback regarding staffing legal requirements and client/candidate experience sections (21:30)\n"},"migrated_from":"contract_meetings","original_id":"ca0bd94d-6c15-4645-bdba-2eb4f54153f1","master_marketer":{"status":"migrated"}}'::jsonb,
