  '[{"text":"Develop and share updated Germany/DACH campaign roadmap document with German team for feedback and translation review (46:30)","completed":false},{"text":"Warm up email domains and LinkedIn outreach profiles using Bettina’s account for German market outreach (14:15)","completed":false},{"text":"Research LinkedIn targeting possibilities based on past company/current company transitions to leverage referrals from personnel movements (43:20)","completed":false},{"text":"Provide Bettina’s and Meiss’s contact info to Colin; add Max to New Norse chat to include him in ongoing communications (49:30)","completed":false},{"text":"Prepare and share relevant usage data, pain points, dashboards to support marketing asset tailoring once the exact needs are clarified (36:30)","completed":false},{"text":"Facilitate ongoing communication with US marketing team to exchange insights on target markets and optimize campaign approach collaboratively (37:15)","completed":false},{"text":"Prepare bilingual (English/German) explainer videos and web pages to support German and broader DACH marketing efforts (46:40)","completed":false},{"text":"Temporarily continue US ad campaigns for 10 more days, then pause post holiday season to focus on German campaigns (52:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Consider testing campaign messaging that emphasizes utilization, active placement, sales skills to resonate with current German pain points and compliance needs (00:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Collaborate to create personalized re-engagement campaigns targeting previous lost deals with tailored messaging referencing past interactions (42:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Coordinate next meeting 30 minutes earlier on Friday to review roadmap and next steps (50:40)","completed":false}]'::jsonb,
