    'https://us02web.zoom.us/j/86093865913?pwd=ajXSuerDGmcROjfezSWYYGsa7iPOWd.1',
    '{"id":"01KC0E1XRYHX1CGS19V7A7G4GR","title":"PTO Exchange Weekly","summary":{"notes":"## **Client Onboarding Video Strategy**\n\nThe team agreed to produce short, standardized demo videos for each new client to improve onboarding clarity and customization.\n\n- **Josh Reinhard proposed creating 30 to 45-second demo videos with a consistent 10-second intro for each client, targeting 30 to 40 new clients next year** to showcase their specific PTO Exchange setup (11:55)  \n    - Colin Costigan confirmed the team can turn these videos around within the same week of recording  \n    - The intro will feature a fixed message with client branding, while the demo will reflect the client’s actual platform interface  \n    - Captions will be added to support hearing-impaired users, maintaining accessibility standards  \n    - This approach balances personalized demos without the complexity of full interactive tutorials, per Colin’s suggestion referencing tools like Storylane  \n\n- **Branding consistency will follow past demo video styles, featuring PTO Exchange branding with client-specific logos embedded in the demo section** (15:04)  \n    - Josh clarified the client logo will appear as it does on their actual dashboard interface, enhancing relatability for employees  \n    - Colin emphasized reusing the existing video structure and branding assets to streamline production  \n    - This approach ensures clear brand identity while tailoring demos to client environments  \n\n## **Marketing Content and Homepage Development**\n\nProgress continues on marketing collateral and website updates, with a focus on content readiness and homepage launch dependencies.\n\n- **Colin updated that new ad creative is in development for the benchmark report, along with copywriting for HR Leaders, Employee Persona, and Industry pages, with Sam Lieberman assigned review responsibilities** (17:19)  \n    - This content pipeline supports upcoming marketing campaigns and targeted messaging segments  \n    - The homepage development is on hold pending FAQ approval to avoid premature exposure of incomplete sections  \n    - Once FAQs are finalized, the team will hide or reveal sections dynamically based on content readiness, maintaining UX quality  \n    - Sam confirmed this phased approach aligns with current development priorities  \n\n## **Automation Stability and Scheduling Coordination**\n\nCurrent automation systems are stable, and scheduling tools are being optimized to improve client engagement workflows.\n\n- **Automation processes are running smoothly with no reported issues from the team, confirming operational stability** (17:57)  \n    - This reliability reduces risk of service disruption and supports scaling plans  \n    - Scheduling integration is being refined with plans to switch from individual Calendly links to a shared booking calendar for better client experience  \n    - Sam will create the shared calendar within the next few days, and Josh will update links accordingly to streamline appointment setting  \n    - This change aims to improve booking efficiency and resource management  \n\n## **Deliverables and Timeline Expectations**\n\nThe team reinforced delivery timelines for key documents and videos to maintain project momentum.\n\n- **Colin committed to delivering the updated FAQ document and marketing deck within the current week to support content and homepage progress** (23:42)  \n    - Josh acknowledged the timeline and will prioritize reviewing the FAQs promptly to avoid bottlenecks  \n    - Josh will record the client demo video today to enable the marketing team’s quick turnaround  \n    - This tight schedule reflects the team’s goal to accelerate onboarding and marketing readiness for Q1  \n    - Clear communication of deadlines ensures alignment across teams and reduces delays  \n\n## **Market Positioning and Strategic Thought**\n\nWhile casual in tone, the discussion revealed strategic intent to balance brand consistency with client-specific customization to improve client experience.\n\n- **Colin emphasized a “happy medium” approach that personalizes client demos without adding complexity, showing a pragmatic balancing of customization and scalability** (14:05)  \n    - The use of existing branding frameworks demonstrates a focus on maintaining a coherent brand image  \n    - Consideration of emerging tools like Storylane indicates openness to future enhancement without immediate commitment  \n    - The team’s approach reflects a strategic mindset prioritizing efficiency and client clarity to support growth targets  \n    - This philosophy supports differentiation by delivering tailored yet consistent client engagement materials","outline":null,"keywords":["PTO Exchange","onboarding videos","client demos","FAQs","Calendly","ad creative"],"overview":"- **Client Onboarding Videos:** Standardized 30-45 second demo videos for 30-40 new clients will enhance onboarding customization.  \n- **Branding Consistency:** Videos will feature PTO Exchange branding with client-specific logos to maintain brand identity and relatability.  \n- **Marketing Content Development:** New ad creatives and content for various audience segments are in progress, with a focus on FAQ completion.  \n- **Automation Stability:** Automation currently stable, scheduling tools will transition to shared calendar links to improve client booking efficiency.  \n- **Deliverables Timelines:** FAQ document and marketing deck are expected this week to support onboarding and marketing readiness for Q1.  \n- **Strategic Market Positioning:** Aim for a balance between customization and scalability while ensuring brand consistency in client engagements.","action_items":"\n**Josh Reinhard**\nRecord onboarding demo video (1.5 minutes) for Salmon Health by end of the week (13:37)\nReview FAQs document sent by Colin (16:58)\n\n**Colin Costigan**\nEdit and brand Josh''s recorded demo videos with consistent PTO Exchange branding and add captions (16:38)\nContinue development of ad creative and copy for HR Leader, Employee Persona, and industry pages; send copy to Sam for review (17:19)\nDeliver the planned deck by the end of the week (23:42)\n\n**Sam Lieberman**\nCreate shared Calendly booking calendar and provide link to Colin for update (17:11)\n"},"duration":24.010000228881836,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"id":1,"name":"Colin Costigan"},{"id":2,"name":"Sam Lieberman"}],"sentences":[{"text":"Hey, Colin, you there?","index":0,"end_time":579.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":576.3,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Can you hear me now?","index":1,"end_time":581.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":580.54,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We can hear you.","index":2,"end_time":582.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":581.62,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Sorry about that.","index":3,"end_time":583.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":582.62,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"No worries.","index":4,"end_time":584.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":583.74,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We had our PR person.","index":5,"end_time":585.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":584.78,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"She.","index":6,"end_time":586.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":585.98,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"She''s like jamming a bunch of stuff in, so Sam''s going to try to join when he can.","index":7,"end_time":589.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":586.34,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Okay, In a minute.","index":8,"end_time":591.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":590.36,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Sounds good.","index":9,"end_time":593.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":592.52,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"How was your weekend?","index":10,"end_time":594.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":593.4,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"How was my weekend?","index":11,"end_time":598.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":597.08,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"It was busy.","index":12,"end_time":598.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":598.04,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Just Christmas time is crazy.","index":13,"end_time":603.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":601.56,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"The weekend.","index":14,"end_time":605.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":604.68,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I feel like it was like 10 minutes.","index":15,"end_time":607,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":605.48,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, we did.","index":16,"end_time":608.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":607.24,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"What do we even do this weekend?","index":17,"end_time":610.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":609.4,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Friday night we had our holiday, our work PTO exchange, holiday dinner.","index":18,"end_time":614.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":610.64,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Saturday, my wife went out with friends and like, didn''t.","index":19,"end_time":620.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":616.21,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Was gonna do an overnight, like, stay at a hotel.","index":20,"end_time":622.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":620.45,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"She ended up coming home at like midnight.","index":21,"end_time":624.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":622.49,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"But I was like.","index":22,"end_time":625.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":624.53,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Took the kids to like, you know, look at Santa Claus.","index":23,"end_time":631.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":625.57,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"And then we like, went to a neighborhood with all the decorations and walked around the neighborhood and stuff.","index":24,"end_time":635.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":631.37,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"And then yesterday we had a gift exchange with friends.","index":25,"end_time":637.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":635.85,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Just like, weekend gone.","index":26,"end_time":639.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":637.97,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Yeah, it''ll happen, that''s for sure.","index":27,"end_time":642.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":640.05,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":28,"end_time":643.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":643.14,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Are you sure?","index":29,"end_time":644.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":644.02,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Is this your first Christmas with a kid?","index":30,"end_time":646.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":644.62,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"I can''t remember.","index":31,"end_time":646.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":646.14,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Yeah, she''ll be.","index":32,"end_time":648.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":647.62,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"She''s turning one year next month.","index":33,"end_time":650.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":648.5,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":34,"end_time":651.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":650.74,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Nice.","index":35,"end_time":651.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":651.38,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"January, baby.","index":36,"end_time":652.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":651.82,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"January baby.","index":37,"end_time":653.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":652.98,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, she was.","index":38,"end_time":654.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":653.9,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Her due date was Valentine''s Day, but she.","index":39,"end_time":657.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":654.9,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"She decided to come a little early.","index":40,"end_time":658.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":657.299,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":41,"end_time":659.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":659.22,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"My purse came like, scary or, you know, a little scary early, so we have one of those too.","index":42,"end_time":666.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":659.7,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Like she was supposed to be mid December and she came in November, you know.","index":43,"end_time":673.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":667.54,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Yeah, one of those.","index":44,"end_time":675.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":674.02,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Yeah, we have.","index":45,"end_time":677.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":676.58,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We have friends that had twins that were born like, I want to say like two and a half, three months early.","index":46,"end_time":685.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":677.54,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, that can happen more with twins, so.","index":47,"end_time":688.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":686.02,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Yeah, but they''re all good now.","index":48,"end_time":690.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":688.26,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, kids are tough.","index":49,"end_time":692.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":690.5,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s so cool.","index":50,"end_time":696.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":694.22,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s like indescribable.","index":51,"end_time":697.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":696.42,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Well, if Sam''s busy, honestly, I''m just going to run through the updates.","index":52,"end_time":705.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":701.02,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I don''t have any new deliverables today.","index":53,"end_time":707.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":705.1,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":54,"end_time":708.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":708.06,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"I have something to ask you if you guys can help us with.","index":55,"end_time":712.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":708.7,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Yeah, did you want to start with that?","index":56,"end_time":714.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":713.18,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, sure.","index":57,"end_time":715.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":715.26,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"One of the things that we''re trying to do now for.","index":58,"end_time":719.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":717.02,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"For incoming clients is create like short digestible videos for them.","index":59,"end_time":725.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":719.35,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Like demoing how to use PTO exchange.","index":60,"end_time":728.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":726.31,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"So like 30, you know, probably 45 second clips.","index":61,"end_time":732.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":728.63,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"What I was hoping was if we can have kind of like a standard 10 seconds at the beginning that''s like pretty consistent for every single client.","index":62,"end_time":745.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":733.75,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"And then a specific 30 to 45 seconds of a demo of like the way that they''re set up that if we could produce a video like that for each of our incoming clients.","index":63,"end_time":759.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":746.2,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"So I would Think we''re going to add.","index":64,"end_time":760.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":759.16,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"You know, ideally, we''re gonna add 30, 40 clients next year, throughout the year, hopefully more.","index":65,"end_time":765.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":760.6,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"But every time we would do it like, the same beginning, and then I would come in, do a quick demo.","index":66,"end_time":770.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":765.24,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"But the demo I would do would be like a minute or a minute and a half.","index":67,"end_time":775.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":771.35,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"And if you guys.","index":68,"end_time":776.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":775.39,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Or we can edit out some of the clicking around in between, so it''s more just like, quick hit.","index":69,"end_time":782.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":776.43,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"This is what you can do on the platform, that would be great.","index":70,"end_time":786.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":782.43,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Yeah, we could absolutely do that.","index":71,"end_time":788.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":787.03,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, so if I record it today in whatever that''s called.","index":72,"end_time":794.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":788.55,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Riverside.","index":73,"end_time":796.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":795.35,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Riverside.","index":74,"end_time":796.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":796.23,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Do you have an idea of, like, how long it would take for a video that short to, like, to put something together?","index":75,"end_time":802.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":798.23,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"I mean, it should be pretty quick.","index":76,"end_time":806.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":803.27,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s not going to always be, like, just based on availability, always the same turnaround.","index":77,"end_time":811.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":807.91,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But, for example, for this, I mean, we should be able to turn that around this week.","index":78,"end_time":817.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":811.95,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, that''d be awesome.","index":79,"end_time":819.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":817.99,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"All right, I''ll get it recorded today.","index":80,"end_time":821.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":819.67,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Like I said, I''m only going to record probably, like, a minute and a half of.","index":81,"end_time":824.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":821.15,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Of demoing.","index":82,"end_time":827.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":825.82,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":83,"end_time":828.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":827.98,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You know, it should just be like P2 exchange.","index":84,"end_time":830.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":828.62,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Like, the beginning should just be like, B2 exchange is A.","index":85,"end_time":834.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":830.74,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Is excited to partner with whatever.","index":86,"end_time":839.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":836.94,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Like, that can just be the text that''s on the screen, and then right there''s like, their logo or whatever.","index":87,"end_time":843.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":839.02,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Yeah, do that.","index":88,"end_time":845.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":843.82,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Yeah, we could absolutely do that.","index":89,"end_time":846.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":845.26,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That kind of reminds me.","index":90,"end_time":847.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":846.42,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I know a while ago we talked about, like, you know, is it worth going down a path, like, even starting with your.","index":91,"end_time":852.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":847.66,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Your biggest clients, like, having a whole page dedicated to them where their employees can go around for tutorial videos or click on buttons.","index":92,"end_time":860.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":852.7,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"This seems like a happy medium.","index":93,"end_time":862.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":861.08,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"There''s also other tools out there, like a. I think I''ve showed you guys this before, but Storylane, where it''s like a personalized demo that they control the pace of.","index":94,"end_time":873.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":862.44,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Have I showed you guys this?","index":95,"end_time":876.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":875.64,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, you have showed us this before, but I don''t think we used it.","index":96,"end_time":880.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":877,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"Yeah, but this is definitely another thing I think would be beneficial, so want to keep that back of our minds as well.","index":97,"end_time":887.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":881.32,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":98,"end_time":891.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":891.42,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, so just let me know when you send that video.","index":99,"end_time":894.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":891.86,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"As far as, like, branding.","index":100,"end_time":895.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":894.38,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Like, do.","index":101,"end_time":899.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":898.3,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"We want it to be basically the same as the last demo videos we produced?","index":102,"end_time":902.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":899.38,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Was the last demo videos we produced.","index":103,"end_time":906.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":904.54,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Let me pull it up.","index":104,"end_time":908.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":907.34,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It was for a specific client.","index":105,"end_time":910.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":908.22,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Is that the light one that you did, Josh?","index":106,"end_time":915.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":913.11,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"I think so.","index":107,"end_time":915.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":915.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":108,"end_time":917.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":917.03,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"But, like, way, like, way shorter than that.","index":109,"end_time":919.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":917.39,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Yeah, I was.","index":110,"end_time":921.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":920.55,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''m just talking, like, strictly about the.","index":111,"end_time":923.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":921.43,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"The branding side of the branding that goes on, like the benefit shift.","index":112,"end_time":926.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":923.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we just branded those last ones, like, just PTO Exchange.","index":113,"end_time":936.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":933.35,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Is that what you''re looking for here as well?","index":114,"end_time":939.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":937.73,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You''re saying, like, at the very top?","index":115,"end_time":948.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":946.85,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Yeah, because if you think about, like, the podcast assets we have, it''s like benefit Shift branding.","index":116,"end_time":953.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":948.61,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":117,"end_time":954.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":954.37,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"So, like, what.","index":118,"end_time":955.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":954.77,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"What it''s going to be here, like, in the inside of, like, the actual.","index":119,"end_time":960.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":955.65,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Where the PTO Exchange logo is not the top left one, but the one that''s on the top dashboard on the.","index":120,"end_time":966.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":961.09,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Not that one.","index":121,"end_time":967.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":966.82,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"The one that''s on the right above United Way.","index":122,"end_time":969.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":967.42,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Oh, okay.","index":123,"end_time":971.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":970.74,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s going to actually be, like, Salmon Health.","index":124,"end_time":974.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":971.9,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Who''s the first one that I''m going to do this for?","index":125,"end_time":975.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":974.34,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"It''s going to be their instance of it with their plan turned on.","index":126,"end_time":979.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":975.94,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":127,"end_time":980.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":980.02,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So if we want it like a big PTO Exchange logo at the top, that''s.","index":128,"end_time":985.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":981.94,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"That''s fine.","index":129,"end_time":986.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":985.5,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"But it''s going to look like what theirs looks like when an employee logs in.","index":130,"end_time":989.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":986.22,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Gotcha.","index":131,"end_time":990.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":989.78,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And do we want the words at the bottom captions?","index":132,"end_time":993.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":990.3,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You know, hearing impaired?","index":133,"end_time":997.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":995.87,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":134,"end_time":998.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":997.47,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Okay, perfect.","index":135,"end_time":998.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":998.03,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Then we already have the structure we need to work from.","index":136,"end_time":1000.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":998.67,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":137,"end_time":1001.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1001.15,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"All right, perfect.","index":138,"end_time":1002.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1001.55,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":139,"end_time":1003.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1003.07,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, just let me know when that''s.","index":140,"end_time":1004.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1003.55,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"When you''ve recorded that.","index":141,"end_time":1006.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1004.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, awesome.","index":142,"end_time":1008.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1007.07,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"And then, Sam, before you join us on Josh, I don''t have any deliverables today, but I do have just some updates.","index":143,"end_time":1014.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1008.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"One I sent over.","index":144,"end_time":1015.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1014.59,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Josh, the document of all the FAQs that we have so far.","index":145,"end_time":1018.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1015.55,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I got to take a look at that.","index":146,"end_time":1019.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1018.46,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"And then also I checked into the.","index":147,"end_time":1021.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1020.14,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We checked in the calendly, and it is just set to your link right now.","index":148,"end_time":1024.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1021.62,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I know you guys were exploring possibly having a shared calendly booking option.","index":149,"end_time":1030.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1026.54,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":150,"end_time":1031.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1030.78,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"If I.","index":151,"end_time":1032.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1031.94,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"If I create that calendar for you.","index":152,"end_time":1034.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1032.42,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"We can swap the link, no problem.","index":153,"end_time":1035.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1034.54,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, okay, I''ll do that.","index":154,"end_time":1037.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1035.94,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"I''ll do that in the next day or so.","index":155,"end_time":1039.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1037.54,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":156,"end_time":1039.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1039.42,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then we''re also updating ad creative for the benchmark report to toss in some new variations and developing the copy for the HR Leaders PA page, the employee Persona page, and getting started on the industry pages as well.","index":157,"end_time":1054.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1040.62,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So it''ll be sending you a lot of copy to review, Sam.","index":158,"end_time":1056.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1054.28,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":159,"end_time":1057.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1056.92,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":160,"end_time":1057.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1057.52,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Is the homepage done development or are we just waiting on the FAQs?","index":161,"end_time":1062.254,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1058.2,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"Waiting on the FAQs.","index":162,"end_time":1064.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1062.426,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then if that''s approved, we''ll just have to hide some sections like we talked about on Thursday that are alluding to, like, the HR page or the employee page, etc.","index":163,"end_time":1074.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1064.76,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":164,"end_time":1074.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1074.16,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Yep.","index":165,"end_time":1075.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1074.6,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s.","index":166,"end_time":1075.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1075.04,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s fine.","index":167,"end_time":1076.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1075.44,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"Sounds good.","index":168,"end_time":1077.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1076.71,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":169,"end_time":1078.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1077.59,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And I think that''s everything from our end.","index":170,"end_time":1082.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1080.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Automation still working great.","index":171,"end_time":1084.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1083.03,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You guys haven''t noticed any issues on your end, right?","index":172,"end_time":1086.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1084.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No, everything seems to be doing all right.","index":173,"end_time":1090.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1088.23,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":174,"end_time":1090.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1090.39,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Okay.","index":175,"end_time":1092.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1091.75,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"Cool.","index":176,"end_time":1093.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1092.55,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Cool.","index":177,"end_time":1094.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1093.91,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Sam, did you have a good weekend?","index":178,"end_time":1095.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1094.55,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I did.","index":179,"end_time":1097.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1096.79,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It was pretty good.","index":180,"end_time":1098.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1098.07,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"Snowed.","index":181,"end_time":1099.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1098.95,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"The Eagles won.","index":182,"end_time":1100.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1099.91,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"Can''t complain.","index":183,"end_time":1102.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1101.43,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"Yeah, I know.","index":184,"end_time":1103.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1102.77,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I was.","index":185,"end_time":1103.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1103.53,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I.","index":186,"end_time":1104.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1103.85,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Guys get a lot of snow in your area?","index":187,"end_time":1107.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1104.09,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"We got a couple inches.","index":188,"end_time":1108.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1107.73,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":189,"end_time":1109.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1108.85,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I was kind of surprised by it.","index":190,"end_time":1111.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1109.73,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"My wife is much more into, like, checking out the weather.","index":191,"end_time":1114.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1111.81,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I had no idea we were even supposed to get hit.","index":192,"end_time":1116.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1114.69,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And I woke up and I was like, oh, all right.","index":193,"end_time":1118.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1116.33,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Whatever the issue is, it, like, melts.","index":194,"end_time":1120.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1118.01,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":195,"end_time":1121.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1121.01,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"I''m in Frederick, Maryland, so, like, as western Maryland as you can get.","index":196,"end_time":1125.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1121.33,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''m 30 minutes from West Virginia and 30 minutes from Pennsylvania.","index":197,"end_time":1129.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1125.49,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Nice.","index":198,"end_time":1131.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1131.35,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"And 45 minutes from D.C. and 45 minutes from Baltimore and Virginia.","index":199,"end_time":1135.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1131.91,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s kind of a nice hub now that I''ve actually listed out all those places.","index":200,"end_time":1140.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1137.43,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But, yeah, I mean, we got.","index":201,"end_time":1144.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1142.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We got a few more inches than I was expecting.","index":202,"end_time":1145.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1144.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"They''re saying it''s gonna be a pretty brutal winner.","index":203,"end_time":1147.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1145.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean, it got cold very fast here, like.","index":204,"end_time":1152.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1149.19,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"Like, it was kind of nice, like, you know, the week before Thanksgiving, and then all of a sudden, it''s, like, 30 degrees.","index":205,"end_time":1159.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1152.87,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":206,"end_time":1159.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1159.28,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"This sucks.","index":207,"end_time":1160.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1160.24,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":208,"end_time":1161.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1161.04,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"The thing that sucks around here is it warms up so much during the day that the snow melts, and then it freezes so fast.","index":209,"end_time":1167.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1161.4,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It just turns everything icy.","index":210,"end_time":1168.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1167.24,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, it was super icy this morning.","index":211,"end_time":1174.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1171.44,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"Yeah, we''re having the opposite issue here.","index":212,"end_time":1176.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1174.64,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"That''s, like.","index":213,"end_time":1177.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1177.2,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"It''s so warm.","index":214,"end_time":1179.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1178,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"That''s why we''re.","index":215,"end_time":1180.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1179.84,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"That''s why the.","index":216,"end_time":1181.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1180.64,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"This, like, all this flooding is happening up here because we''re getting, like, real rain, which we normally don''t get.","index":217,"end_time":1187.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1181.6,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"We get, like, drizzle, but it''s been, like, 55 to 60 degrees.","index":218,"end_time":1192.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1187.91,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"So all the snow from the mountains is just melting enough that it''s flooding the rivers, and then we''re getting dumped on rain, and it''s, like, nuts.","index":219,"end_time":1203.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1193.71,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Not.","index":220,"end_time":1203.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1203.47,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Not, like, where I live, but 20.","index":221,"end_time":1206.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1203.71,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"My clients sent me a picture.","index":222,"end_time":1207.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1206.11,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think she''s in Oregon, if I remember correctly.","index":223,"end_time":1210.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1207.67,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"She sent me a picture of, like, all this flooding that''s going on under the bridges.","index":224,"end_time":1218.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1212.36,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":225,"end_time":1219.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1219.48,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Wow.","index":226,"end_time":1220.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1219.92,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"There''s a.","index":227,"end_time":1221.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1220.84,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"So kind of close to our office, but, like, like, 30 minutes from where I live.","index":228,"end_time":1227.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1221.88,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Is this the town called Snoqualmie?","index":229,"end_time":1229.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1227.36,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"And we have some friends that live up there.","index":230,"end_time":1230.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1229.08,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"And if you live, like, up on the top of the ridge, it''s like totally fine.","index":231,"end_time":1233.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1230.48,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Which is where our friends live.","index":232,"end_time":1234.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1233.12,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"But if you live down the sides, it''s getting a crush.","index":233,"end_time":1237.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1234.24,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"And they have these.","index":234,"end_time":1238.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1237.49,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"This huge waterfall.","index":235,"end_time":1239.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1238.45,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"It''s like the biggest waterfall in the Pacific Northwest.","index":236,"end_time":1242.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1239.85,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"And normally it''s just like, you know, a cool looking waterfall.","index":237,"end_time":1246.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1242.49,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"It is just like huge logs, like huge are getting caught, swept up into the river and then going over the side of the falls and it looks like Niagara Falls right now.","index":238,"end_time":1257.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1246.73,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"It''s like.","index":239,"end_time":1258.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1257.69,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"It''s nuts.","index":240,"end_time":1258.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1258.01,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"That''s crazy.","index":241,"end_time":1259.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1259.17,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":242,"end_time":1260.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1259.89,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":243,"end_time":1261.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1260.53,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Side by side where it''s like normal Snoqualmie Falls.","index":244,"end_time":1264.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1261.65,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"And then what it was last week and it like doesn''t even look at the same place.","index":245,"end_time":1267.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1264.72,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":246,"end_time":1268.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1268.24,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"That makes me think of Sam.","index":247,"end_time":1270.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1268.68,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I don''t know if you know, like Ellicott City.","index":248,"end_time":1272,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1270.52,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":249,"end_time":1273.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1272.88,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"But like, remember 10 years ago they got hit with like a massive flood and then all the businesses and everything shut down.","index":250,"end_time":1279.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1273.92,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then they opened up, I think a year later and a flood happened again on the open day and like closed all the businesses back down.","index":251,"end_time":1286.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1279.8,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s terrible the way the city.","index":252,"end_time":1289.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1287.52,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, we had a pretty bad flood.","index":253,"end_time":1293.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1291.03,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"I mean, it''s got.","index":254,"end_time":1295.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1294.79,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"It had to be.","index":255,"end_time":1296.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1295.75,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"It might have been before COVID at this point.","index":256,"end_time":1299.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1297.03,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"It was a couple of years ago, but I 76 or 676, which is like the main expressway that like cuts through the city and it kind of like.","index":257,"end_time":1309.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1299.11,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"It like dips down.","index":258,"end_time":1311.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1309.99,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"It''s not a tunnel, but it dips down below.","index":259,"end_time":1313.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1311.55,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"The river line was like totally flooded.","index":260,"end_time":1317.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1313.55,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"So there was like literally like a river crossing through the middle of Philadelphia.","index":261,"end_time":1322.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1317.05,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"And like, people.","index":262,"end_time":1322.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1322.05,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"People were like swimming in it and like jumping in and like putting raft inner tubes in there.","index":263,"end_time":1328.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1323.17,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"And I had friends who''s like, you know, they had to evacuate their apartment buildings because they are right on like the Schuylkill river banks like that.","index":264,"end_time":1336.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1328.89,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"It was.","index":265,"end_time":1337.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1336.77,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"And they were like getting rescued by boats and stuff.","index":266,"end_time":1340.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1337.17,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"It was pretty crazy.","index":267,"end_time":1342.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1340.93,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"I. I''m curious about my own house now that I talk about it.","index":268,"end_time":1346.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1342.05,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"I''m pretty close to the Schuylkill River.","index":269,"end_time":1347.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1346.25,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"I wonder if that''s gonna affect me ever.","index":270,"end_time":1349.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1347.77,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"Maybe check that out.","index":271,"end_time":1351.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1350.93,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Sam, I actually thought of you over the weekend.","index":272,"end_time":1354.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1352.53,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I saw a post and it was if Stranger Things actors were from Delco.","index":273,"end_time":1359.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1354.17,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s a good one.","index":274,"end_time":1361.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1360.45,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"There we go.","index":275,"end_time":1361.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1361.29,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"The accents were cracking me up.","index":276,"end_time":1364.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1363.01,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Gotta watch.","index":277,"end_time":1365.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1364.45,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"Yeah, you gotta watch Ask Task.","index":278,"end_time":1368.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1365.01,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"Yeah, the Mark Ruffalo show with all the Delco accents.","index":279,"end_time":1372.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1368.69,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"They do a good job with the Delco accents, I gotta say.","index":280,"end_time":1374.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1372.36,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"It''s not too ridiculous.","index":281,"end_time":1376.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1374.92,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No, it''s.","index":282,"end_time":1377.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1376.76,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"It''s.","index":283,"end_time":1378.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1377.96,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"It''s the accents are good.","index":284,"end_time":1379.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1378.32,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"I mean, I was saying earlier, like, they go to Rita''s water ice.","index":285,"end_time":1383.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1379.52,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"They.","index":286,"end_time":1383.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1383.64,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"They have a flyer shirt on.","index":287,"end_time":1385.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1383.92,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"It''s very Philly.","index":288,"end_time":1386.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1385.36,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s like, almost.","index":289,"end_time":1387.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1386.6,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s a little.","index":290,"end_time":1388.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1387.64,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s what you''re saying.","index":291,"end_time":1389.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1388.359,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You''re like, every single thing.","index":292,"end_time":1390.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1389.32,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"People are proud of Philly.","index":293,"end_time":1392.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1391.32,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"Philli''s got pride.","index":294,"end_time":1393.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1392.68,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s for sure.","index":295,"end_time":1394.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1393.56,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yep.","index":296,"end_time":1395.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1394.76,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"So, awesome.","index":297,"end_time":1397.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1395.64,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"All right, well, yeah, I''ll be in touch with those updates, and then, Josh, let me know when you record that video and have a chance to look at those FAQs.","index":298,"end_time":1405.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1397.24,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I''ll get on that as soon as I can.","index":299,"end_time":1407.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1405.43,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":300,"end_time":1407.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1407.19,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right, thank you guys very much.","index":301,"end_time":1409.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1407.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right, thanks.","index":302,"end_time":1409.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1409.11,"speaker_name":"Sam Lieberman"},{"text":"Sorry if I miss this.","index":303,"end_time":1415.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1413.75,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"The.","index":304,"end_time":1415.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1415.27,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"The deck.","index":305,"end_time":1416.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1415.63,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"When do you think you guys are going to have that?","index":306,"end_time":1418.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1416.47,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Say that?","index":307,"end_time":1419.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1419.19,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Yeah, we should have that this week as well.","index":308,"end_time":1424.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1422.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":309,"end_time":1425.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1425.11,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Well, I didn''t.","index":310,"end_time":1426.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1425.83,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"I know that was the plan last week.","index":311,"end_time":1427.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1426.47,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"I didn''t know if that changed at all.","index":312,"end_time":1428.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1427.59,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":313,"end_time":1430.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1429.83,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"Cool.","index":314,"end_time":1431.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1430.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":315,"end_time":1431.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1431.35,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"},{"text":"I''ll see you guys.","index":316,"end_time":1432.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1432.07,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"See you.","index":317,"end_time":1433.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1432.83,"speaker_name":"Josh Reinhard"}],"dateString":"2025-12-15T20:30:00.000Z","host_email":"colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com","meeting_link":"https://us02web.zoom.us/j/86093865913?pwd=ajXSuerDGmcROjfezSWYYGsa7iPOWd.1","participants":["josh@ptoexchange.com,colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com,sam@ptoexchange.com","josh@ptoexchange.com","sam@ptoexchange.com"],"transcript_url":"https://app.fireflies.ai/view/01KC0E1XRYHX1CGS19V7A7G4GR","organizer_email":"colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com"}'::jsonb,
    '{"label":"positive","confidence":0.88,"bullets":["Agreed to produce short branded demo videos for new clients with rapid turnaround expectations.","Josh to record first client-specific demo today with standardized intro and send to Colin.","Colin confirmed video edits, captions, and branding can align with prior PTO Exchange materials.","FAQ documentation shared; pending Josh’s review before homepage sections are finalized.","Team updating ad creative and HR-focused copy; Sam to review upcoming content batches."],"highlights":[{"quote":"Yeah, we could absolutely do that.","speaker":"Colin Costigan"},{"quote":"Okay, that''d be awesome.","speaker":"Josh Reinhard"},{"quote":"No, everything seems to be doing all right.","speaker":"Sam Lieberman"}],"topics":["delivery","branding","client onboarding","copy","video"],"model":"openai/gpt-4-turbo","version":1,"generated_at":"2025-12-16T00:00:00Z"}'::jsonb,
    '{"fireflies_summary":{"notes":"## **Client Onboarding Video Strategy**\n\nThe team agreed to produce short, standardized demo videos for each new client to improve onboarding clarity and customization.\n\n- **Josh Reinhard proposed creating 30 to 45-second demo videos with a consistent 10-second intro for each client, targeting 30 to 40 new clients next year** to showcase their specific PTO Exchange setup (11:55)  \n    - Colin Costigan confirmed the team can turn these videos around within the same week of recording  \n    - The intro will feature a fixed message with client branding, while the demo will reflect the client’s actual platform interface  \n    - Captions will be added to support hearing-impaired users, maintaining accessibility standards  \n    - This approach balances personalized demos without the complexity of full interactive tutorials, per Colin’s suggestion referencing tools like Storylane  \n\n- **Branding consistency will follow past demo video styles, featuring PTO Exchange branding with client-specific logos embedded in the demo section** (15:04)  \n    - Josh clarified the client logo will appear as it does on their actual dashboard interface, enhancing relatability for employees  \n    - Colin emphasized reusing the existing video structure and branding assets to streamline production  \n    - This approach ensures clear brand identity while tailoring demos to client environments  \n\n## **Marketing Content and Homepage Development**\n\nProgress continues on marketing collateral and website updates, with a focus on content readiness and homepage launch dependencies.\n\n- **Colin updated that new ad creative is in development for the benchmark report, along with copywriting for HR Leaders, Employee Persona, and Industry pages, with Sam Lieberman assigned review responsibilities** (17:19)  \n    - This content pipeline supports upcoming marketing campaigns and targeted messaging segments  \n    - The homepage development is on hold pending FAQ approval to avoid premature exposure of incomplete sections  \n    - Once FAQs are finalized, the team will hide or reveal sections dynamically based on content readiness, maintaining UX quality  \n    - Sam confirmed this phased approach aligns with current development priorities  \n\n## **Automation Stability and Scheduling Coordination**\n\nCurrent automation systems are stable, and scheduling tools are being optimized to improve client engagement workflows.\n\n- **Automation processes are running smoothly with no reported issues from the team, confirming operational stability** (17:57)  \n    - This reliability reduces risk of service disruption and supports scaling plans  \n    - Scheduling integration is being refined with plans to switch from individual Calendly links to a shared booking calendar for better client experience  \n    - Sam will create the shared calendar within the next few days, and Josh will update links accordingly to streamline appointment setting  \n    - This change aims to improve booking efficiency and resource management  \n\n## **Deliverables and Timeline Expectations**\n\nThe team reinforced delivery timelines for key documents and videos to maintain project momentum.\n\n- **Colin committed to delivering the updated FAQ document and marketing deck within the current week to support content and homepage progress** (23:42)  \n    - Josh acknowledged the timeline and will prioritize reviewing the FAQs promptly to avoid bottlenecks  \n    - Josh will record the client demo video today to enable the marketing team’s quick turnaround  \n    - This tight schedule reflects the team’s goal to accelerate onboarding and marketing readiness for Q1  \n    - Clear communication of deadlines ensures alignment across teams and reduces delays  \n\n## **Market Positioning and Strategic Thought**\n\nWhile casual in tone, the discussion revealed strategic intent to balance brand consistency with client-specific customization to improve client experience.\n\n- **Colin emphasized a “happy medium” approach that personalizes client demos without adding complexity, showing a pragmatic balancing of customization and scalability** (14:05)  \n    - The use of existing branding frameworks demonstrates a focus on maintaining a coherent brand image  \n    - Consideration of emerging tools like Storylane indicates openness to future enhancement without immediate commitment  \n    - The team’s approach reflects a strategic mindset prioritizing efficiency and client clarity to support growth targets  \n    - This philosophy supports differentiation by delivering tailored yet consistent client engagement materials","outline":null,"keywords":["PTO Exchange","onboarding videos","client demos","FAQs","Calendly","ad creative"],"overview":"- **Client Onboarding Videos:** Standardized 30-45 second demo videos for 30-40 new clients will enhance onboarding customization.  \n- **Branding Consistency:** Videos will feature PTO Exchange branding with client-specific logos to maintain brand identity and relatability.  \n- **Marketing Content Development:** New ad creatives and content for various audience segments are in progress, with a focus on FAQ completion.  \n- **Automation Stability:** Automation currently stable, scheduling tools will transition to shared calendar links to improve client booking efficiency.  \n- **Deliverables Timelines:** FAQ document and marketing deck are expected this week to support onboarding and marketing readiness for Q1.  \n- **Strategic Market Positioning:** Aim for a balance between customization and scalability while ensuring brand consistency in client engagements.","action_items":"\n**Josh Reinhard**\nRecord onboarding demo video (1.5 minutes) for Salmon Health by end of the week (13:37)\nReview FAQs document sent by Colin (16:58)\n\n**Colin Costigan**\nEdit and brand Josh''s recorded demo videos with consistent PTO Exchange branding and add captions (16:38)\nContinue development of ad creative and copy for HR Leader, Employee Persona, and industry pages; send copy to Sam for review (17:19)\nDeliver the planned deck by the end of the week (23:42)\n\n**Sam Lieberman**\nCreate shared Calendly booking calendar and provide link to Colin for update (17:11)\n"},"migrated_from":"contract_meetings","original_id":"0df5cd8e-461b-4199-88bb-6f1c9117e5c8","master_marketer":{"status":"migrated"}}'::jsonb,
