 was like 30 or 3,000 total.","index":209,"end_time":753.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":750.01,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"We filter to 500.","index":210,"end_time":755.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":753.72,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"And then this is without an AI layer yet.","index":211,"end_time":758.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":755.96,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"So a lot.","index":212,"end_time":760.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":759.88,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"A lot more construction titles that we were pulling in from the.","index":213,"end_time":764.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":760.92,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Non hyperscalers.","index":214,"end_time":767.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":766.36,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"But definitely not the, like the.","index":215,"end_time":773.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":772.12,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"The range of titles that we were seeing in the other organizations.","index":216,"end_time":778.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":773.88,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"I think what''s hard.","index":217,"end_time":780.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":779.3,"speaker_name":"Rob"},{"text":"Is we might need to separate.","index":218,"end_time":785.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":782.5,"speaker_name":"Rob"},{"text":"So like a project manager is actually pretty relevant for a gc, but it''s not for the hyperscalers or corporation.","index":219,"end_time":794.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":786.9,"speaker_name":"Rob"},{"text":"So I think that''s the.","index":220,"end_time":797.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":795.7,"speaker_name":"Rob"},{"text":"So we''re getting construction project managers, but we''re not maybe getting like.","index":221,"end_time":801.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":797.78,"speaker_name":"Rob"},{"text":"Project managers or something like that.","index":222,"end_time"