w, I was built.","index":469,"end_time":1583.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1580.63,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"But yeah, I mean in those cases when we are using a template page and you have to figure out like, where''s this field going?","index":470,"end_time":1589.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1583.77,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Or if I change this, you know what happens.","index":471,"end_time":1592.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1589.73,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Sometimes it does require just trying to figure out what you want to do and, and figure out what the, the website does.","index":472,"end_time":1600.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1593.53,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Because, you know, WordPress is all a hierarchy for.","index":473,"end_time":1603.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1600.41,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"For.","index":474,"end_time":1603.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1603.53,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s more like there''s like a drop down and it''ll be like template one, template two, template three, three.","index":475,"end_time":1609.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1605.13,"speaker_name":"Rob"},{"text":"And it''s like I can''t.","index":476,"end_time":1611.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1610.1,"speaker_name":"Rob"},{"text":"If I could find where those are housed and to see what those are.","index":477,"end_time":1615.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1611.22,"speaker_name":"Rob"},{"text":"Right.","index":478,"end_time":1616.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1616.02,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Because it allows you to do the drop down.","index":479,"end_time":1618.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1616.38,"speaker_name":"Rob"},{"text":"But at least I did find in the couple hours I spent with it yesterday, like, okay, here''s where you see where someone created template one and it''s saved.","index":480,"end_time":1627.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1618.22,"speaker_name":"Rob"},{"text":"So you, you''re kind of guessing based off looking at the site, but it''s fine.","index":481,"end_time":1631.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1627.22,"speaker_name":"Rob"},{"text":"I''m.","index":482,"end_time":1632.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1631.7,"speaker_name":"Rob"},{"text":"I, I think I''ll manage around that by.","index":483,"end_time":1634.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1632.26,"speaker_name":"Rob"},{"text":"Since the overall goal is to simplify, I think I''ll be able to manage around that one.","index":484,"end_time":1640.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1635.47,"speaker_name":"Rob"},{"text":"It''s really more like.","index":485,"end_time":1642.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1640.91,"speaker_name":"Rob"},{"text":"And you.","index":486,"end_time":1644.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1643.95,"speaker_name":"Rob"},{"text":"I can always restore anything back to what it was.","index":487,"end_time":1647.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1644.43,"speaker_name":"Rob"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s the main thing.","index":488,"end_time":1649.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1648.19,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, it''s really more.","index":489,"end_time":1652.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1649.87,"speaker_name":"Rob"},{"text":"It''s really more of the deleting thing, which I can ask specific question.","index":490,"end_time":1655.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1652.03,"speaker_name":"Rob"},{"text":"Yep.","index":491,"end_time":1656.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1656.27,"speaker_name":"Rob"},{"text":"Let me.","index":492,"end_time":1658.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1657.95,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"I can do.","index":493,"end_time":1659.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1658.51,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Here.","index":494,"end_time":1661.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1661.48,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"I will show you whe